83 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
84 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::applyBTinv( vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type& dPhiIn,
85  vec3D_dbl_Type& dPhiOut,
86  SmallMatrix<SC>& Binv){
87  UN dim = Binv.size();
88  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiIn->size(); w++){
89  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiIn->at(w).size(); i++) {
90  for (UN d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
91  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++) {
92  dPhiOut[w][i][d1] += dPhiIn->at(w).at(i).at(d2) * Binv[d2][d1];
93  }
94  }
95  }
96  }
97 }
110 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
111 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLinearElasticity(int dim,
112  string FEType,
113  int degree,
114  int dofs,
115  MultiVectorPtr_Type d_rep,
116  BlockMatrixPtr_Type &A,
117  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type &resVec,
118  ParameterListPtr_Type params,
119  bool reAssemble,
120  string assembleMode,
121  bool callFillComplete,
122  int FELocExternal){
123 
124  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(0)->getElementsC();
125 
126  int dofsElement = elements->getElement(0).getVectorNodeList().size();
127 
128  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(0)->getPointsRepeated();
129 
130  MapConstPtr_Type mapVel = domainVec_.at(0)->getMapRepeated();
131 
132  vec_dbl_Type solution(0);
133  vec_dbl_Type solution_d;
134 
135  vec_dbl_Type rhsVec;
136 
139  int numNodes=6;
140  if(dim==3){
141  numNodes=10;
142  }
143  tuple_disk_vec_ptr_Type problemDisk = Teuchos::rcp(new tuple_disk_vec_Type(0));
144  tuple_ssii_Type displacement ("Displacement",FEType,dofs,numNodes);
145  problemDisk->push_back(displacement);
146 
147  if(assemblyFEElements_.size()== 0)
148  initAssembleFEElements("LinearElasticity",problemDisk,elements, params,pointsRep);
149  else if(assemblyFEElements_.size() != elements->numberElements())
150  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( true, std::logic_error, "Number Elements not the same as number assembleFE elements." );
151 
152  MultiVectorPtr_Type resVec_d = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(0)->getMapVecFieldRepeated(), 1 ) );
153 
154  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type resVecRep = Teuchos::rcp( new BlockMultiVector_Type(1) );
155  resVecRep->addBlock(resVec_d,0);
156 
157  SmallMatrixPtr_Type elementMatrix;
158  for (UN T=0; T<assemblyFEElements_.size(); T++) {
159  vec_dbl_Type solution(0);
160 
161  solution_d = getSolution(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), d_rep,dofs);
162 
163  solution.insert( solution.end(), solution_d.begin(), solution_d.end() );
164 
165  assemblyFEElements_[T]->updateSolution(solution);
166 
167  assemblyFEElements_[T]->assembleJacobian();
168 
169  elementMatrix = assemblyFEElements_[T]->getJacobian();
170 
171  assemblyFEElements_[T]->advanceNewtonStep();
172 
173 
174  addFeBlock(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), mapVel, 0, 0, problemDisk);
175 
176  }
177  if (callFillComplete)
178  A->getBlock(0,0)->fillComplete( domainVec_.at(0)->getMapVecFieldUnique(),domainVec_.at(0)->getMapVecFieldUnique());
179 
180 
181 
182 
183 }

277 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
278 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyNonLinearElasticity(int dim,
279  string FEType,
280  int degree,
281  int dofs,
282  MultiVectorPtr_Type d_rep,
283  BlockMatrixPtr_Type &A,
284  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type &resVec,
285  ParameterListPtr_Type params,

312  problemDisk->push_back(displacement);
313 
314  if(assemblyFEElements_.size()== 0)

330  assemblyFEElements_[T]->updateParameter("E",eModVecA[T]);
331  assemblyFEElements_[T]->assembleJacobian();

333  addFeBlock(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), map, 0, 0, problemDisk);

361 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
362 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::addFeBlockMv(BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type &res, vec_dbl_Type rhsVec, FiniteElement elementBlock, int dofs){
363 
364  Teuchos::ArrayRCP<SC> resArray_block = res->getBlockNonConst(0)->getDataNonConst(0);
365 
366  vec_LO_Type nodeList_block = elementBlock.getVectorNodeList();
367 
368  for(int i=0; i< nodeList_block.size() ; i++){
369  for(int d=0; d<dofs; d++)
370  resArray_block[nodeList_block[i]*dofs+d] += rhsVec[i*dofs+d];
371  }
372 }

385 // das wird aus problem/specific/NavierStokes aufgerufen
386 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
387 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyNavierStokes(int dim,
388  string FETypeVelocity,
389  string FETypePressure,
390  int degree,
391  int dofsVelocity,
392  int dofsPressure,
393  MultiVectorPtr_Type u_rep,
394  MultiVectorPtr_Type p_rep,
395  BlockMatrixPtr_Type &A,
396  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type &resVec,
397  SmallMatrix_Type coeff,
398  ParameterListPtr_Type params,
399  bool reAssemble,
400  string assembleMode,
401  bool callFillComplete,
402  int FELocExternal){
403 
404 
405  UN FElocVel = checkFE(dim,FETypeVelocity); // Checks for different domains which belongs to a certain fetype
406  UN FElocPres = checkFE(dim,FETypePressure); // Checks for different domains which belongs to a certain fetype
407 
408  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getElementsC();
409 
410  ElementsPtr_Type elementsPres = domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getElementsC();
411 
412  int dofsElement = elements->getElement(0).getVectorNodeList().size();
413 
414  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getPointsRepeated();
415 
416  MapConstPtr_Type mapVel = domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapRepeated();
417 
418  MapConstPtr_Type mapPres = domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getMapRepeated();
419 
420  vec_dbl_Type solution(0);
421  vec_dbl_Type solution_u;
422  vec_dbl_Type solution_p;
423  vec_dbl_Type solution_viscosity;
424 
425 
426  vec_dbl_Type rhsVec;
427 
430  int dofs;
431  int numVelo=3;
432  if(FETypeVelocity == "P2")
433  numVelo=6;
434  if(dim==3){
435  numVelo=4;
436  if(FETypeVelocity == "P2")
437  numVelo=10;
438  }
439  tuple_disk_vec_ptr_Type problemDisk = Teuchos::rcp(new tuple_disk_vec_Type(0));
440  tuple_ssii_Type vel ("Velocity",FETypeVelocity,dofsVelocity,numVelo);
441  tuple_ssii_Type pres ("Pressure",FETypePressure,dofsPressure,dim+1);
442  problemDisk->push_back(vel);
443  problemDisk->push_back(pres);
444 
445  if(assemblyFEElements_.size()== 0){
446  //bool newtonian = params->sublist("Material").get("Newtonian",true);
447  if(params->sublist("Material").get("Newtonian",true) == false)
448  initAssembleFEElements("NavierStokesNonNewtonian",problemDisk,elements, params,pointsRep); // In case of non Newtonian Fluid
449  // jumps inside FEDDLib/FEEDLIB_LEA/source/FEDDLib/feddlib/core/AceFemAssembly/specific/AssembleFENavierStokesNonNewtonian_def.hpp:9
450  else
451  initAssembleFEElements("NavierStokes",problemDisk,elements, params,pointsRep);
452  }
453  else if(assemblyFEElements_.size() != elements->numberElements())
454  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( true, std::logic_error, "Number Elements not the same as number assembleFE elements." );
455 
456  //SmallMatrixPtr_Type elementMatrix =Teuchos::rcp( new SmallMatrix_Type( dofsElement));
457 
458  MultiVectorPtr_Type resVec_u = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldRepeated(), 1 ) );
459  MultiVectorPtr_Type resVec_p = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getMapRepeated(), 1 ) );
460 
461  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type resVecRep = Teuchos::rcp( new BlockMultiVector_Type( 2) );
462  resVecRep->addBlock(resVec_u,0);
463  resVecRep->addBlock(resVec_p,1);
464 
465 
466  // we have to add viscosity solution of on each local node to a global solution vector of the viscosity
467  MultiVectorPtr_Type Sol_viscosity = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapRepeated(), 1 ) );
468  BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type visco_output = Teuchos::rcp( new BlockMultiVector_Type(1) );
469  visco_output->addBlock(Sol_viscosity,0);
470  //assemblyFEElements_[0]->materialModel->echoParams();
471 
472 
473  for (UN T=0; T<assemblyFEElements_.size(); T++) {
474 
475  vec_dbl_Type solution(0);
476 
477  solution_u = getSolution(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), u_rep,dofsVelocity); // get the solution inside an element on the nodes
478  solution_p = getSolution(elementsPres->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), p_rep,dofsPressure);
479 
480  solution.insert( solution.end(), solution_u.begin(), solution_u.end() ); // here we insert the solution
481  solution.insert( solution.end(), solution_p.begin(), solution_p.end() );
482 
483  assemblyFEElements_[T]->updateSolution(solution); // here we update the value of the solutions inside an element
484 
485  SmallMatrixPtr_Type elementMatrix;
486 
487  if(assembleMode == "Jacobian"){
489  assemblyFEElements_[T]->assembleJacobian(); // so here we construct the element matrices and we compute the viscosity
490 
491  elementMatrix = assemblyFEElements_[T]->getJacobian();
492 
493  if(params->sublist("Material").get("Newtonian",true) == false)
494  {
495  solution_viscosity = assemblyFEElements_[T]->getViscositySolution();
496  // solution_viscosity = assemblyFEElements_[T]->solutionViscosity_;
497  // so eine funktion brauche
498  addFeBlockVis(visco_output, solution_viscosity, elements->getElement(T), dofsPressure );
499  }
500  assemblyFEElements_[T]->advanceNewtonStep(); // n genereal non linear solver step
501 
502  if(reAssemble)
503  addFeBlock(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), mapVel, 0, 0, problemDisk);
504  else
505  addFeBlockMatrix(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), mapVel, mapPres, problemDisk);
506  }
507  if(assembleMode == "FixedPoint"){
508 
509  AssembleFENavierStokesPtr_Type elTmp = Teuchos::rcp_dynamic_cast<AssembleFENavierStokes_Type>(assemblyFEElements_[T] );
510 
511  elTmp->assembleFixedPoint();
512 
513  elementMatrix = elTmp->getFixedPointMatrix();
514 
515  assemblyFEElements_[T]->advanceNewtonStep(); // n genereal non linear solver step
516 
517  if(reAssemble)
518  addFeBlock(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), mapVel, 0, 0, problemDisk);
519  else
520  addFeBlockMatrix(A, elementMatrix, elements->getElement(T), mapVel, mapPres, problemDisk);
521 
522  }
523  if(assembleMode == "Rhs"){
524  AssembleFENavierStokesPtr_Type elTmp = Teuchos::rcp_dynamic_cast<AssembleFENavierStokes_Type>(assemblyFEElements_[T] );
525  elTmp->setCoeff(coeff);// Coeffs from time discretization. Right now default [1][1] // [0][0]
526  assemblyFEElements_[T]->assembleRHS();
527  rhsVec = assemblyFEElements_[T]->getRHS();
528  addFeBlockMv(resVecRep, rhsVec, elements->getElement(T),elementsPres->getElement(T), dofsVelocity,dofsPressure);
529  }
530 
531 
532  } // end loop over all elements
533 
534  // if etc.....
535  this->visco_output_= visco_output;
536 
537  if (callFillComplete && reAssemble && assembleMode != "Rhs" )
538  A->getBlock(0,0)->fillComplete( domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldUnique(),domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldUnique());
539  else if(callFillComplete && !reAssemble && assembleMode != "Rhs"){
540  A->getBlock(0,0)->fillComplete();
541  A->getBlock(1,0)->fillComplete(domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldUnique(),domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getMapUnique());
542  A->getBlock(0,1)->fillComplete(domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getMapUnique(),domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldUnique());
543  A->getBlock(1,1)->fillComplete();
544  }
545 
546  if(assembleMode == "Rhs"){
547 
548  MultiVectorPtr_Type resVecUnique_u = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(FElocVel)->getMapVecFieldUnique(), 1 ) );
549  MultiVectorPtr_Type resVecUnique_p = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type( domainVec_.at(FElocPres)->getMapUnique(), 1 ) );
550 
551  resVecUnique_u->putScalar(0.);
552  resVecUnique_p->putScalar(0.);
553 
554  resVecUnique_u->exportFromVector( resVec_u, true, "Add" );
555  resVecUnique_p->exportFromVector( resVec_p, true, "Add" );
556 
557  resVec->addBlock(resVecUnique_u,0);
558  resVec->addBlock(resVecUnique_p,1);
559  }
560 
561 
562 }

575 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
576 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::addFeBlockMv(BlockMultiVectorPtr_Type &res, vec_dbl_Type rhsVec, FiniteElement elementBlock1,FiniteElement elementBlock2, int dofs1, int dofs2 ){
577 
578  Teuchos::ArrayRCP<SC> resArray_block1 = res->getBlockNonConst(0)->getDataNonConst(0);
579 
580  Teuchos::ArrayRCP<SC> resArray_block2 = res->getBlockNonConst(1)->getDataNonConst(0);
581 
582  vec_LO_Type nodeList_block1 = elementBlock1.getVectorNodeList();
583 
584  vec_LO_Type nodeList_block2 = elementBlock2.getVectorNodeList();
585 
586  for(int i=0; i< nodeList_block1.size() ; i++){
587  for(int d=0; d<dofs1; d++)
588  resArray_block1[nodeList_block1[i]*dofs1+d] += rhsVec[i*dofs1+d];
589  }
590  int offset = nodeList_block1.size()*dofs1;
591 
592  for(int i=0; i < nodeList_block2.size(); i++){
593  for(int d=0; d<dofs2; d++)
594  resArray_block2[nodeList_block2[i]*dofs2+d] += rhsVec[i*dofs2+d+offset];
595  }
596 
597 }

639 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
640 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::addFeBlockMatrix(BlockMatrixPtr_Type &A, SmallMatrixPtr_Type elementMatrix, FiniteElement element, MapConstPtr_Type mapFirstRow,MapConstPtr_Type mapSecondRow, tuple_disk_vec_ptr_Type problemDisk){
641 
642  int numDisk = problemDisk->size();
643 
644  int dofs1 = std::get<2>(problemDisk->at(0));
645  int dofs2 = std::get<2>(problemDisk->at(1));
646 
647  int numNodes1 = std::get<3>(problemDisk->at(0));
648  int numNodes2=std::get<3>(problemDisk->at(1));
649 
650  int dofsBlock1 = dofs1*numNodes1;
651  int dofsBlock2 = dofs2*numNodes2;
652 
653  Teuchos::Array<SC> value1( numNodes1, 0. );
654  Teuchos::Array<GO> columnIndices1( numNodes1, 0 );
655 
656  for (UN i=0; i < numNodes1 ; i++) {
657  for(int di=0; di<dofs1; di++){
658  GO row =GO (dofs1* mapFirstRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(i) )+di);
659  for(int d=0; d<dofs1; d++){
660  for (UN j=0; j < columnIndices1.size(); j++){
661  columnIndices1[j] = GO ( dofs1 * mapFirstRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(j) ) + d );
662  value1[j] = (*elementMatrix)[dofs1*i+di][dofs1*j+d];
663  }
664  A->getBlock(0,0)->insertGlobalValues( row, columnIndices1(), value1() ); // Automatically adds entries if a value already exists
665  }
666  }
667  }
668 
669  Teuchos::Array<SC> value2( 1, 0. );
670  Teuchos::Array<GO> columnIndex( 1, 0. );
671  Teuchos::Array<GO> rowIndex( 1, 0. );
672 
673  int offset= numNodes1*dofs1;
674  //Teuchos::ArrayView<const LO> indices;
675  //Teuchos::ArrayView<const SC> values;
676 
677  for (UN j=0; j < numNodes2; j++){
678  rowIndex[0] = GO ( mapSecondRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(j) ) );
679  for (UN i=0; i < numNodes1 ; i++) {
680  for(int d=0; d<dofs1; d++){
681  value2[0] = (*elementMatrix)[i*dofs1+d][offset+j];
682  columnIndex[0] =GO (dofs1* mapFirstRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(i) )+d);
683 
684  A->getBlock(1,0)->insertGlobalValues( rowIndex[0], columnIndex(), value2() ); // Automatically adds entries if a value already exists
685  A->getBlock(0,1)->insertGlobalValues( columnIndex[0], rowIndex(), value2() ); // Automatically adds entries if a value already exists
686  }
687  }
688  }
689 }

703 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
704 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::addFeBlock(BlockMatrixPtr_Type &A, SmallMatrixPtr_Type elementMatrix, FiniteElement element, MapConstPtr_Type mapRow, int row, int column, tuple_disk_vec_ptr_Type problemDisk){
705 
706  int dofs1 = std::get<2>(problemDisk->at(row));
707 
708  int numNodes1 = std::get<3>(problemDisk->at(row));
709 
710  int dofsBlock1 = dofs1*numNodes1;
711 
712  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( numNodes1, 0. );
713  Teuchos::Array<GO> columnIndices( numNodes1, 0 );
714 
715  for (UN i=0; i < numNodes1 ; i++) {
716  for(int di=0; di<dofs1; di++){
717  GO rowID =GO (dofs1* mapRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(i) )+di);
718  for(int d=0; d<dofs1; d++){
719  for (UN j=0; j < columnIndices.size(); j++){
720  columnIndices[j] = GO ( dofs1 * mapRow->getGlobalElement( element.getNode(j) ) + d );
721  value[j] = (*elementMatrix)[dofs1*i+di][dofs1*j+d];
722  }
723  A->getBlock(row,column)->insertGlobalValues( rowID, columnIndices(), value() ); // Automatically adds entries if a value already exists
724  }
725  }
726  }
727 }

813 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
814 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::applyBTinv( vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type& dPhiIn,
815  vec3D_dbl_Type& dPhiOut,
816  const SmallMatrix<SC>& Binv){
817  UN dim = Binv.size();
818  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiIn->size(); w++){
819  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiIn->at(w).size(); i++) {
820  for (UN d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
821  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++) {
822  dPhiOut[w][i][d1] += dPhiIn->at(w).at(i).at(d2) * Binv[d2][d1];
823  }
824  }
825  }
826  }
827 }

833 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
834 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyIdentity(MatrixPtr_Type &A){
835  Teuchos::Array<SC> value(1, Teuchos::ScalarTraits<SC>::one() );
836  Teuchos::Array<GO> index(1);
837  MapConstPtr_Type map = A->getMap();
838  for (int i=0; i<A->getNodeNumRows(); i++) {
839  index[0] = map->getGlobalElement( i );
840  A->insertGlobalValues( index[0], index(), value() );
841  }
842  A->fillComplete();
843 }

845 // Assembling the nonlinear reaction part of Reaction-Diffusion equation
846 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
847 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyReactionTerm(int dim,
848  std::string FEType,
849  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
850  MultiVectorPtr_Type u,
851  bool callFillComplete,
852  std::vector<SC>& funcParameter,
853  RhsFunc_Type reactionFunc){
854 
855  //TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( u->getNumVectors()>1, std::logic_error, "Implement for numberMV > 1 ." );
856  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
857 
858  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
859 
860  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
861 
862  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
863 
864  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
865 
866  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
867  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
868 
869  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Std); //Elementwise assembly of grad u
870 
871  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Std, extraDeg);
872 
873  getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
874 
875  // We have a scalar value of concentration in each point
876  vec_dbl_Type uLoc( weights->size() , -1. );
877  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > uArray = u->getData(0);
878 
879  std::vector<double> valueFunc(1);
880 
881  SC* paras = &(funcParameter[0]);
882 
883  SC detB;
884  SC absDetB;
885  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
886  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
887 
888  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
889  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
890  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
891  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
892 
893  // Building u
894  for (int w=0; w<phi->size(); w++){ //quadpoints
895  uLoc[w] = 0.;
896  for (int i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) { // points of element
897  LO index = elements->getElement(T).getNode(i);
898  uLoc[w] += uArray[index] * phi->at(w).at(i);
899  }
900  }
901 
902  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
903  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
904  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
905  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
906  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
907  value[j] += weights->at(w) * uLoc[w] * (*phi)[w][i] ;
908  }
909  reactionFunc(&value[j], &valueFunc[0] ,paras);
910 
911  value[j] *= valueFunc[0] * absDetB;
912  if (setZeros_ && std::fabs(value[j]) < myeps_) {
913  value[j] = 0.;
914  }
915  indices[j] = GO( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ));
916 
917  }
918  GO row = GO ( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) );
919  /*if( domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getComm()->getRank() == 1){
920  cout << " Inserting in Row " << row ;
921  for(int j=0 ; j< indices.size() ; j++)
922  cout << " with indices " << indices[j] << " " ;
923  cout << "on rank " <<domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getComm()->getRank() << endl;
924  }*/
925 
926  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
927  if( domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getComm()->getRank() == 1)
928  cout << " Inserted " << row << endl;
929  }
930  }
931 
932  if (callFillComplete)
933  A->fillComplete();
934 }

937 // Assembling the nonlinear reaction part of Reaction-Diffusion equation
938 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
939 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLinearReactionTerm(int dim,
940  std::string FEType,
941  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
942  bool callFillComplete,
943  std::vector<SC>& funcParameter,
944  RhsFunc_Type reactionFunc){
945 
946  //TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( u->getNumVectors()>1, std::logic_error, "Implement for numberMV > 1 ." );
947  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
948 
949  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
950 
951  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
952 
953  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
954 
955  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
956 
957  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
958  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
959 
960  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Std); //Elementwise assembly of grad u
961 
962  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Std, extraDeg);
963 
964  getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
965 
966  std::vector<double> valueFunc(1);
967 
968  SC* paras = &(funcParameter[0]);
969 
970  SC detB;
971  SC absDetB;
972  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
973  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
974 
975  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
976  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
977  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
978  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
979 
980  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
981  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
982  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
983  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
984  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
985  value[j] += weights->at(w) * (*phi)[w][j] * (*phi)[w][i] ;
986  }
987  reactionFunc(&value[j], &valueFunc[0] ,paras);
988 
989  value[j] *= valueFunc[0] * absDetB;
990  if (setZeros_ && std::fabs(value[j]) < myeps_) {
991  value[j] = 0.;
992  }
993  indices[j] = GO( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ));
994 
995  }
996  GO row = GO ( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) );
997 
998  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
999 
1000  }
1001  }
1002 
1003  if (callFillComplete)
1004  A->fillComplete();
1005 }

1007 // Assembling the nonlinear reaction part of Reaction-Diffusion equation
1008 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1009 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyDReactionTerm(int dim,
1010  std::string FEType,
1011  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1012  MultiVectorPtr_Type u,
1013  bool callFillComplete,
1014  std::vector<SC>& funcParameter,
1015  RhsFunc_Type reactionFunc){
1016 
1017  //TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( u->getNumVectors()>1, std::logic_error, "Implement for numberMV > 1 ." );
1018  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
1019 
1020  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1021 
1022  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1023 
1024  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1025 
1026  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1027 
1028  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
1029  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1030  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1031 
1032  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Std); //Elementwise assembly of grad u
1033 
1034  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Std, extraDeg);
1035 
1036  getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1037 
1038  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1039 
1040  // We have a scalar value of concentration in each point
1041  vec2D_dbl_Type duLoc( weights->size() ,vec_dbl_Type(dim ,-1. ));
1042  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > uArray = u->getData(0);
1043 
1044  std::vector<double> valueFunc(1);
1045 
1046  SC* paras = &(funcParameter[0]);
1047 
1048  SC detB;
1049  SC absDetB;
1050  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1051  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1052 
1053  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1054 
1055 
1056  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
1057  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
1058  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1059 
1060  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
1061  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv );
1062 
1063  for (int w=0; w<dPhiTrans.size(); w++){ //quads points
1064  for (int i=0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++) {
1065  LO index = elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ;
1066  for (int d2=0; d2<dim; d2++)
1067  duLoc[w][d2] += uArray[index] * dPhiTrans[w][i][d2];
1068  }
1069 
1070  }
1071 
1072 
1073  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
1074  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
1075  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
1076  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1077  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++){
1078  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
1079  value[j] += weights->at(w) * duLoc[w][d2] * (*phi)[w][i] ;
1080  }
1081  }
1082  reactionFunc(&value[j], &valueFunc[0] ,paras);
1083 
1084  value[j] *= valueFunc[0] * absDetB;
1085  if (setZeros_ && std::fabs(value[j]) < myeps_) {
1086  value[j] = 0.;
1087  }
1088  indices[j] = GO( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ));
1089 
1090  }
1091  GO row = GO ( map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) );
1092  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1093  }
1094  }
1095 
1096  if (callFillComplete)
1097  A->fillComplete();
1098 }

1101 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1102 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLaplaceDiffusion(int dim,
1103  std::string FEType,
1104  int degree,
1105  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1106  vec2D_dbl_Type diffusionTensor,
1107  bool callFillComplete,
1108  int FELocExternal){
1109  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
1110  UN FEloc;
1111  if (FELocExternal<0)
1112  FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1113  else
1114  FEloc = FELocExternal;
1115 
1116  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1117 
1118  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1119 
1120  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1121 
1122  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1123  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1124 
1125  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Grad,Grad);
1126  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1127 
1128  SC detB;
1129  SC absDetB;
1130  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1131  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1132  GO glob_i, glob_j;
1133  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
1134  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
1135 
1136 
1137  SmallMatrix<SC> diffusionT(dim);
1138  // Linear Diffusion Tensor
1139  if(diffusionTensor.size()==0 || diffusionTensor.size() < dim ){
1140  vec2D_dbl_Type diffusionTensor(3,vec_dbl_Type(3,0));
1141  for(int i=0; i< dim; i++){
1142  diffusionT[i][i]=1.;
1143  }
1144  //diffusionTensor = Teuchos::rcp( new MultiVector_Type(domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementMap(), 1 ) );
1145  //diffusionTensor->putScalar(1.);
1146  }
1147 
1148  for(int i=0; i< dim; i++){
1149  for(int j=0; j<dim; j++){
1150  diffusionT[i][j]=diffusionTensor[i][j];
1151  }
1152  }
1153  //Teuchos::ArrayRCP< SC > linearDiff = diffusionTensor->getDataNonConst( 0 );
1154  //cout << "Assembly Info " << "num Elements " << elements->numberElements() << " num Nodes " << pointsRep->size() << endl;
1155  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1156 
1157  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
1158  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
1159  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1160 
1161  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
1162  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv );
1163 
1164  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTransDiff( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
1165  applyDiff( dPhiTrans, dPhiTransDiff, diffusionT );
1166 
1167  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++) {
1168  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0. );
1169  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0 );
1170 
1171  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1172  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiTrans.size(); w++) {
1173  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++){
1174  value[j] += weights->at(w) * dPhiTrans[w][i][d] * dPhiTransDiff[w][j][d];
1175  }
1176  }
1177  value[j] *= absDetB;
1178  indices[j] = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) );
1179  }
1180  GO row = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) );
1181 
1182  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1183  }
1184 
1185 
1186  }
1187  if (callFillComplete)
1188  A->fillComplete();
1189 
1190 }
1191 
1192 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1193 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::applyDiff( vec3D_dbl_Type& dPhiIn,
1194  vec3D_dbl_Type& dPhiOut,
1195  SmallMatrix<SC>& diffT){
1196  UN dim = diffT.size();
1197  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiIn.size(); w++){
1198  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiIn[w].size(); i++) {
1199  for (UN d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
1200  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++) {
1201  dPhiOut[w][i][d1] += dPhiIn[w][i][d2]* diffT[d2][d1];
1202  }
1203  }
1204  }
1205  }
1206 }

1208 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1209 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyAceGenTPM( MatrixPtr_Type &A00,
1210  MatrixPtr_Type &A01,
1211  MatrixPtr_Type &A10,
1212  MatrixPtr_Type &A11,
1213  MultiVectorPtr_Type &F0,
1214  MultiVectorPtr_Type &F1,
1215  MapPtr_Type &mapRepeated1,
1216  MapPtr_Type &mapRepeated2,
1217  ParameterListPtr_Type parameterList,
1218  MultiVectorPtr_Type u_repeatedNewton,
1219  MultiVectorPtr_Type p_repeatedNewton,
1220  MultiVectorPtr_Type u_repeatedTime,
1221  MultiVectorPtr_Type p_repeatedTime,
1222  bool update,
1223  bool updateHistory)
1224 {
1225 
1226 
1227  std::string tpmType = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("TPM Type","Biot");
1228 
1229  int dim = domainVec_[0]->getDimension();
1230  int idata = 1; //= we should init this
1231  int ic = -1; int ng = -1;
1232 
1233  //ed.hp:history previous (timestep); previous solution (velocity and acceleration)
1234  //ed.ht:? same length as hp
1235  ElementsPtr_Type elements1 = domainVec_[0]->getElementsC();
1236  ElementsPtr_Type elements2 = domainVec_[1]->getElementsC();
1237 
1238  int sizeED = 24; /* 2D case for P2 elements:
1239  12 velocities, 12 accelerations (2 dof per P2 node)
1240  */
1241  if (dim==3)
1242  sizeED = 60;/* 3D case for P2 elements:
1243  30 velocities, 30 accelerations (3 dof per P2 node)
1244  */
1245  if (ed_.size()==0){
1246  for (UN T=0; T<elements1->numberElements(); T++)
1247  ed_.push_back( Teuchos::rcp(new DataElement( sizeED )) );
1248  }
1249 
1250  std::vector<ElementSpec> es_vec( parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Number of materials",1) , ElementSpec());
1251  vec2D_dbl_Type dataVec( parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Number of materials",1), vec_dbl_Type(6,0.) );
1252 
1253  for (int i=0; i<dataVec.size(); i++) {
1254  if (tpmType == "Biot") {
1255  if (dim==2) {
1256  dataVec[i][0] = parameterList->sublist("Timestepping Parameter").get("Newmark gamma",0.5);
1257  dataVec[i][1] = parameterList->sublist("Timestepping Parameter").get("Newmark beta",0.25);
1258  dataVec[i][2] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("initial volume fraction solid material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.5); //do we need this?
1259  dataVec[i][3] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Darcy parameter material"+std::to_string(i+1),1.e-2);
1260  dataVec[i][4] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Youngs modulus material"+std::to_string(i+1),60.e6);
1261  dataVec[i][5] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Poisson ratio material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.3);
1262  }
1263  else if (dim==3) {
1264  dataVec[i].resize(12);
1265  dataVec[i][0] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Youngs modulus material"+std::to_string(i+1),2.e5);
1266  dataVec[i][1] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Poisson ratio material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.3);

1268  dataVec[i][3] = 0.; //body force y
1269  dataVec[i][4] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("body force z"+std::to_string(i+1),0.);; //body force z
1270  dataVec[i][5] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("initial volume fraction solid material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.67);

1273  dataVec[i][8] = 1000.; //effective density fluid?

1278  }
1279 
1280 
1281  else if (tpmType == "Biot-StVK") {
1282  dataVec[i][0] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Youngs modulus material"+std::to_string(i+1),60.e6);
1283  dataVec[i][1] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Poisson ratio material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.3);
1284  dataVec[i][2] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("initial volume fraction solid material"+std::to_string(i+1),0.5); //do we need this?
1285  dataVec[i][3] = parameterList->sublist("Parameter").get("Darcy parameter material"+std::to_string(i+1),1.e-2);

1300  }

1304  GO sizePhaseGlobal = A00->getMap()->getMaxAllGlobalIndex()+1;

1322  // ap ist die Loesung im letzten Zeitschritt.

1460  else if (i%dim==1)

1462  else if (i%dim==2)

1470  else if (i%dim==1)
1471  fValues0[ dim*index+1 ] += p[ i ];
1472  else if (i%dim==2)
1473  fValues0[ dim*index+2 ] += p[ i ];

1486  else if (j%dim==1)

1499  }
1500 
1501

1503  GO row = mapRepeated2->getGlobalElement( index2 );

1508  }

1510  }

1522

1531 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1532 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyMass(int dim,
1533  std::string FEType,
1534  std::string fieldType,
1535  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1536  bool callFillComplete){
1537 
1538  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( FEType == "P0", std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0" );
1539  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1540 
1541  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1542 
1543  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1544 
1545  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1546 
1547  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
1548  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1549 
1550  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Std,Std);
1551 
1552  getPhi( phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg );
1553 
1554  SC detB;
1555  SC absDetB;
1556  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1557  GO glob_i, glob_j;
1558  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
1559  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
1560 
1561  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1562 
1563  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
1564  detB = B.computeDet( );
1565  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1566 
1567  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
1568  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
1569  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
1570  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1571  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
1572  value[j] += weights->at(w) * (*phi)[w][i] * (*phi)[w][j];
1573 
1574  }
1575  value[j] *= absDetB;
1576  if (!fieldType.compare("Scalar")) {
1577  indices[j] = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) );
1578  }
1579 
1580  }
1581  if (!fieldType.compare("Scalar")) {
1582  GO row = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) );
1583  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1584  }
1585  else if (!fieldType.compare("Vector")) {
1586  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++) {
1587  for (int j=0; j<indices.size(); j++) {
1588  indices[j] = (GO) ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d );
1589  }
1590  GO row = (GO) ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d );
1591  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1592  }
1593  }
1594  else
1595  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(true, std::logic_error, "Specify valid vieldType for assembly of mass matrix.");
1596  }
1597 
1598  }
1599 
1600  if (callFillComplete)
1601  A->fillComplete();
1602 }
1603 
1604 
1605 // Ueberladung der Assemblierung der Massematrix fuer FSI, da
1606 // checkFE sonst auch fuer das Strukturproblem FEloc = 1 liefert (= Fluid)
1607 // und somit die welche domain und Map in der Assemblierung genutzt wird.
1608 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1609 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyMass(int dim,

1611  std::string fieldType,

1614  bool callFillComplete){

1617 
1618  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();

1620  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1621 
1622  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1623 
1624  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
1625  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1626 
1627  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Std,Std);
1628 
1629  getPhi( phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg );
1630 
1631  SC detB;
1632  SC absDetB;
1633  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);

1639 
1640  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
1641  detB = B.computeDet( );
1642  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1643 
1644  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
1645  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
1646  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
1647  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1648  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
1649  value[j] += weights->at(w) * (*phi)[w][i] * (*phi)[w][j];
1650  }
1651  value[j] *= absDetB;
1652  if (!fieldType.compare("Scalar")) {
1653  indices[j] = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) );
1654  }
1655 
1656  }

1661  else if (!fieldType.compare("Vector")) {

1674 
1675  }

1681 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1682 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLaplace(int dim,
1683  std::string FEType,
1684  int degree,
1685  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1686  bool callFillComplete,
1687  int FELocExternal){
1688  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
1689  UN FEloc;
1690  if (FELocExternal<0)
1691  FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1692  else
1693  FEloc = FELocExternal;
1694 
1695  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1696 
1697  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1698 
1699  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1700 
1701  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1702  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1703 
1704  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Grad,Grad);
1705  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1706 
1707  SC detB;
1708  SC absDetB;
1709  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1710  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1711  GO glob_i, glob_j;
1712  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
1713  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
1714 
1715  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1716 
1717  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
1718  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
1719  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1720 
1721  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
1722  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv );
1723  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++) {
1724  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0. );
1725  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0 );
1726  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1727  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiTrans.size(); w++) {
1728  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++){
1729  value[j] += weights->at(w) * dPhiTrans[w][i][d] * dPhiTrans[w][j][d];
1730  }
1731  }
1732  value[j] *= absDetB;
1733  indices[j] = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) );
1734  }
1735  GO row = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) );
1736 
1737  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1738  }
1739 
1740 
1741  }
1742  if (callFillComplete)
1743  A->fillComplete();
1744 
1745 }
1746 
1747 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1748 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLaplaceVecField(int dim,
1749  std::string FEType,
1750  int degree,
1751  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1752  bool callFillComplete){
1753 
1754  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P1-disc" || FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0 or P1-disc");
1755  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1756 
1757  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1758 
1759  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1760 
1761  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1762 
1763  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1764  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1765 
1766  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Grad,Grad);
1767 
1768  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1769 
1770  SC detB;
1771  SC absDetB;
1772  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1773  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1774  GO glob_i, glob_j;
1775  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
1776  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
1777 
1778 
1779  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1780 
1781  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
1782  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
1783  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1784 
1785  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
1786  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv );
1787 
1788  for (UN i=0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++) {
1789  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0. );
1790  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( dPhiTrans[0].size(), 0 );
1791  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
1792  for (UN w=0; w<dPhiTrans.size(); w++) {
1793  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++)
1794  value[j] += weights->at(w) * dPhiTrans[w][i][d] * dPhiTrans[w][j][d];
1795  }
1796  value[j] *= absDetB;
1797  if (setZeros_ && std::fabs(value[j]) < myeps_) {
1798  value[j] = 0.;
1799  }
1800  }
1801  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++) {
1802  for (UN j=0; j < indices.size(); j++)
1803  indices[j] = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d );
1804 
1805  GO row = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d );
1806  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1807  }
1808  }
1809  }
1810  if (callFillComplete)
1811  A->fillComplete();
1812 }
1813 //this assembly used blas matrix-matrix multiplications. It determines the local stiffness matrix at once, but has some overhead due to zero off-diagonal blocks which are computed.
1814 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1815 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLaplaceVecFieldV2(int dim,
1816  std::string FEType,
1817  int degree,
1818  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1819  bool callFillComplete){
1820 
1821  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
1822  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1823 
1824  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1825 
1826  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1827 
1828  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1829 
1830  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1831  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1832 
1833  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Grad,Grad);
1834 
1835  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1836 
1837  Teuchos::BLAS<int, SC> teuchosBLAS;
1838 
1839  int nmbQuadPoints = dPhi->size();
1840  int nmbScalarDPhi = dPhi->at(0).size();
1841  int nmbAllDPhi = nmbScalarDPhi * dim;
1842  int nmbAllDPhiAllQaud = nmbQuadPoints * nmbAllDPhi;
1843  int sizeLocStiff = dim*dim;
1844  Teuchos::Array<SmallMatrix<double> > dPhiMat( nmbAllDPhiAllQaud, SmallMatrix<double>(dim) );
1845  this->buildFullDPhi( dPhi, dPhiMat ); //builds matrix from gradient of scalar phi
1846 
1847 
1848  SC detB;
1849  SC absDetB;
1850  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1851  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1852  GO glob_i, glob_j;
1853  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
1854  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
1855 
1856  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
1857 
1858  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
1859  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
1860  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
1861 
1862  Teuchos::Array<SmallMatrix<double> > allDPhiMatTrans( dPhiMat.size(), SmallMatrix<double>() );
1863 
1864  for (int i=0; i<allDPhiMatTrans.size(); i++) {
1865  SmallMatrix<double> res = dPhiMat[i] * Binv;
1866  allDPhiMatTrans[i] = res;
1867  }
1868 
1869  SmallMatrix<double> locStiffMat( nmbAllDPhi, 0. );
1870 
1871  for (int p=0; p<nmbQuadPoints; p++){
1872 
1873  double* allDPhiBlas = new double[ nmbAllDPhi * sizeLocStiff ];
1874 
1875  int offset = p * nmbAllDPhi;
1876  int offsetInArray = 0;
1877  for (int i=0; i<nmbAllDPhi; i++) {
1878  fillMatrixArray( allDPhiMatTrans[ offset + i ], allDPhiBlas, "rows",offsetInArray );
1879  offsetInArray += sizeLocStiff;
1880  }
1881 
1882  double* locStiffMatBlas = new double[ nmbAllDPhi * nmbAllDPhi ];
1883 
1884  teuchosBLAS.GEMM (Teuchos::TRANS, Teuchos::NO_TRANS, nmbAllDPhi, nmbAllDPhi, sizeLocStiff, 1., allDPhiBlas, sizeLocStiff/*lda of A not trans(A)! Otherwise result is wrong*/, allDPhiBlas, sizeLocStiff, 0., locStiffMatBlas, nmbAllDPhi);
1885 
1886  for (int i=0; i<nmbAllDPhi; i++) {
1887  for (int j=0; j<nmbAllDPhi; j++) {
1888  locStiffMat[i][j] += weights->at(p) * locStiffMatBlas[ j * nmbAllDPhi + i ];
1889  }
1890  }
1891 
1892  delete [] allDPhiBlas;
1893  delete [] locStiffMatBlas;
1894 
1895  }
1896 
1897  for (UN i=0; i < nmbScalarDPhi; i++) {
1898  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( nmbAllDPhi, 0. );
1899  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( nmbAllDPhi, 0 );
1900  for (UN d=0; d<dim; d++) {
1901  for (UN j=0; j < nmbScalarDPhi; j++){
1902  value[ j * dim + d ] = absDetB * locStiffMat[dim * i + d][j];
1903  indices[ j * dim + d ] = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d );
1904  }
1905  GO row = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d );
1906  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
1907  }
1908  }
1909  }
1910  if (callFillComplete)
1911  A->fillComplete();
1912 }

1914 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
1915 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyElasticityJacobianAndStressAceFEM(int dim,
1916  std::string FEType,
1917  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
1918  MultiVectorPtr_Type &f,
1919  MultiVectorPtr_Type u,
1920  ParameterListPtr_Type pList,
1921  double C,
1922  bool callFillComplete){
1923  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::runtime_error, "Not implemented for P0");
1924  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
1925 
1926 
1927  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
1928  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
1929 
1930  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
1931  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
1932  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
1933 
1934  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Grad,Grad);
1935 
1936  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
1937 
1938  SC detB;
1939  SC absDetB;
1940  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
1941  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
1942 
1943  Teuchos::BLAS<int, SC> teuchosBLAS;
1944 
1945  int nmbQuadPoints = dPhi->size();
1946  int nmbScalarDPhi = dPhi->at(0).size();
1947  int nmbAllDPhi = nmbScalarDPhi * dim;
1948  int nmbAllDPhiAllQaud = nmbQuadPoints * nmbAllDPhi;
1949  int sizeLocStiff = dim*dim;
1950  Teuchos::Array<SmallMatrix<SC> > dPhiMat( nmbAllDPhiAllQaud, SmallMatrix<SC>(dim) );
1951 
1952  this->buildFullDPhi( dPhi, dPhiMat ); //builds matrix from gradient of scalar phi
1953 
1954  std::string material_model = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("Material model","Neo-Hooke");
1955 
1956  double poissonRatio = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("Poisson Ratio",0.4);
1957  double mue = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("Mu",2.0e+6);
1958  double mue1 = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("Mu1",2.0e+6);
1959  double mue2 = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("Mu2",2.0e+6);
1960  // Berechne daraus nun E (Youngsches Modul) und die erste Lamé-Konstante \lambda
1961  double E = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("E",3.0e+6); // For StVK mue_*2.*(1. + poissonRatio_);
1962  double E1 = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("E1",3.0e+6); // For StVK mue_*2.*(1. + poissonRatio_);
1963  double E2 = pList->sublist("Parameter").get("E2",3.0e+6); // For StVK mue_*2.*(1. + poissonRatio_);
1964 
1965  if (material_model=="Saint Venant-Kirchhoff") {
1966  E = mue*2.*(1. + poissonRatio);
1967  E1 = mue1*2.*(1. + poissonRatio);
1968  E2 = mue2*2.*(1. + poissonRatio);
1969  }
1970 
1971  // For StVK (poissonRatio*E)/((1 + poissonRatio)*(1 - 2*poissonRatio));
1972  double lambda = (poissonRatio*E)/((1 + poissonRatio)*(1 - 2*poissonRatio));
1973  double lambda1 = (poissonRatio*E1)/((1 + poissonRatio)*(1 - 2*poissonRatio));
1974  double lambda2 = (poissonRatio*E2)/((1 + poissonRatio)*(1 - 2*poissonRatio));
1975 
1976  if (dim == 2){
1977  double* v;
1978  if(!material_model.compare("Saint Venant-Kirchhoff"))
1979  v = new double[154];
1980  else
1981  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(true, std::logic_error, "Only Saint Venant-Kirchhoff in 2D.");
1982

1984  for (int i=0; i<2; i++)
1985  Pmat[i] = new double[2];
1986

1988  for (int i=0; i<2; i++)
1989  F[i] = new double[2];
1990

1992  for (int i=0; i<2; i++){
1993  Amat[i] = new double**[2];
1994  for (int j=0; j<2; j++) {
1995  Amat[i][j] = new double*[2];
1996  for (int k=0; k<2; k++)
1997  Amat[i][j][k] = new double[2];
1998  }
1999  }

2006  for (int T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
2007

2257  mr3d(v, &E, &poissonRatio, &C, F, Pmat, Amat);
2258  else if ( !material_model.compare("Saint Venant-Kirchhoff") )
2259  stvk3d(v, &lambda, &mue, F, Pmat, Amat);
2260 
2261  SmallMatrix<SC> Aloc(dim*dim);
2262  for (int i=0; i<3; i++) {
2263  for (int j=0; j<3; j++) {
2264  for (int k=0; k<3; k++) {
2265  for (int l=0; l<3; l++) {
2266  Aloc[ 3 * i + j ][ 3 * k + l ] = Amat[i][j][k][l];
2267  }
2268  }
2269  }
2270  }
2271 
2272  double* aceFEMFunc = new double[ sizeLocStiff * sizeLocStiff ];
2273  double* allDPhiBlas = new double[ nmbAllDPhi * sizeLocStiff ];
2274 
2275  //jacobian
2276  double* resTmp = new double[ nmbAllDPhi * sizeLocStiff ];
2277  // all_dPhiMat_Binv: quadpoints -> basisfunction vector field
2278  fillMatrixArray(Aloc, aceFEMFunc, "cols"); //blas uses column-major
2279 
2280  int offset = p * nmbAllDPhi;
2281  int offsetInArray = 0;
2282  for (int i=0; i<nmbAllDPhi; i++) {
2283  fillMatrixArray( all_dPhiMat_Binv[ offset + i ], allDPhiBlas, "rows",offsetInArray );
2284  offsetInArray += sizeLocStiff;
2285  }
2286 
2287  teuchosBLAS.GEMM (Teuchos::NO_TRANS, Teuchos::NO_TRANS, sizeLocStiff, nmbAllDPhi, sizeLocStiff, 1., aceFEMFunc, sizeLocStiff, allDPhiBlas, sizeLocStiff, 0., resTmp, sizeLocStiff);
2288 
2289 
2290  double* locStiffMatBlas = new double[ nmbAllDPhi * nmbAllDPhi ];
2291 
2292  teuchosBLAS.GEMM (Teuchos::TRANS, Teuchos::NO_TRANS, nmbAllDPhi, nmbAllDPhi, sizeLocStiff, 1., allDPhiBlas, sizeLocStiff/*lda of A not trans(A)! Otherwise result is wrong*/, resTmp, sizeLocStiff, 0., locStiffMatBlas, nmbAllDPhi);
2293 
2294  for (int i=0; i<nmbAllDPhi; i++) {
2295  for (int j=0; j<nmbAllDPhi; j++)
2296  locStiffMat[i][j] += weights->at(p) * locStiffMatBlas[ j * nmbAllDPhi + i ];
2297  }
2298 
2299  delete [] resTmp;
2300  delete [] locStiffMatBlas;
2301 
2302 
2303  //stress
2304  double* fArray = new double[ sizeLocStiff ];
2305  for (int i=0; i<dim; i++) {
2306  for (int j=0; j<dim; j++) {
2307  fArray[i * dim + j] = Pmat[i][j]; //is this correct?
2308  }
2309  }
2310 
2311  double* res = new double[ nmbAllDPhi ];
2312  teuchosBLAS.GEMV(Teuchos::TRANS, sizeLocStiff, nmbAllDPhi, 1., allDPhiBlas, sizeLocStiff, fArray, 1, 0., res, 1);
2313  for (int i=0; i<locStresses.size(); i++) {
2314  locStresses[i] += weights->at(p) * res[i];
2315  }
2316 
2317  delete [] res;
2318  delete [] aceFEMFunc;
2319  delete [] allDPhiBlas;
2320  delete [] fArray;
2321  }
2322 
2323  for (int i=0; i<nmbScalarDPhi; i++) {
2324  for (int d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
2325 
2326  LO rowLO = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + d1;
2327  SC v = absDetB * locStresses[ dim * i + d1 ];
2328  fValues[rowLO] += v;
2329 
2330  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( nmbAllDPhi, 0. );
2331  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( nmbAllDPhi, 0 );
2332  LO counter = 0;
2333  for (UN j=0; j < nmbScalarDPhi; j++){
2334  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++) {
2335  indices[counter] = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d2 );
2336  value[counter] = absDetB * locStiffMat[dim*i+d1][dim*j+d2];
2337 
2338  counter++;
2339  }
2340  }
2341  GO row = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d1 );
2342  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
2343  }
2344  }
2345  }
2346 
2347  delete [] v;
2348  for (int i=0; i<3; i++)
2349  delete [] Pmat[i];
2350  delete [] Pmat;
2351  for (int i=0; i<3; i++)
2352  delete [] F[i];
2353  delete [] F;
2354 
2355  for (int i=0; i<3; i++){
2356  for (int j=0; j<3; j++) {
2357  for (int k=0; k<3; k++)
2358  delete [] Amat[i][j][k];
2359  delete [] Amat[i][j];
2360  }
2361  delete [] Amat[i];
2362  }
2363  delete [] Amat;
2364 
2365  }
2366  if (callFillComplete)
2367  A->fillComplete();
2368 
2369 }

2762 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
2763 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyAdvectionVecField(int dim,

2844  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
2845  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
2846  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
2847 
2848  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Std); //Elementwise assembly of grad u
2849 
2850  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Std, extraDeg);
2851 
2852  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
2853  getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
2854  SC detB;
2855  SC absDetB;
2856  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
2857  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
2858  GO glob_i, glob_j;
2859  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
2860  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
2861 
2862  vec2D_dbl_Type uLoc( dim, vec_dbl_Type( weights->size() , -1. ) );
2863  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > uArray = u->getData(0);
2864 
2865  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
2866 
2867  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
2868  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
2869  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);

2892

2896  value[j] = 0.;

2900  GO glob_j = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) );
2901  }

2903  for (UN j=0; j < indices.size(); j++)
2904  indices[j] = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d );
2905 
2906  GO row = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d );
2907  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
2908  }
2909  }
2910  }
2911  }
2912

2914  A->fillComplete();

2917 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
2918 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyAdvectionInUVecField(int dim,
2919  std::string FEType,
2920  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
2921  MultiVectorPtr_Type u,
2922  bool callFillComplete){
2923 
2924  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION( u->getNumVectors()>1, std::logic_error, "Implement for numberMV > 1 ." );
2925  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
2926  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
2927 
2928  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
2929 
2930  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
2931 
2932  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
2933 
2934  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
2935  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
2936  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
2937 
2938  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Grad); //Elementwise assembly of u
2939 
2940  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Std, Std, extraDeg);
2941 
2942  getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
2943  getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
2944 
2945  SC detB;
2946  SC absDetB;
2947  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
2948  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
2949  GO glob_i, glob_j;
2950  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
2951  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
2952 
2953  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > uArray = u->getData(0);
2954 
2955  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
2956 
2957  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
2958  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
2959  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
2960 
2961  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
2962  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv );
2963 
2964  std::vector<SmallMatrix<SC> > duLoc( weights->size(), SmallMatrix<SC>(dim) ); //for all quad points p_i each matrix is [u_x * grad Phi(p_i), u_y * grad Phi(p_i), u_z * grad Phi(p_i) (if 3D) ], duLoc[w] = [[phixx;phixy],[phiyx;phiyy]] (2D)
2965 
2966  for (int w=0; w<dPhiTrans.size(); w++){ //quads points
2967  for (int d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
2968  for (int i=0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++) {
2969  LO index = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + d1;
2970  for (int d2=0; d2<dim; d2++)
2971  duLoc[w][d2][d1] += uArray[index] * dPhiTrans[w][i][d2];
2972  }
2973  }
2974  }
2975 
2976  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
2977  for (UN d1=0; d1<dim; d1++) {
2978  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( dim*phi->at(0).size(), 0. ); //These are value (W_ix,W_iy,W_iz)
2979  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( dim*phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
2980  for (UN j=0; j < phi->at(0).size(); j++) {
2981  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++){
2982  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
2983  value[ dim * j + d2 ] += weights->at(w) * duLoc[w][d2][d1] * (*phi)[w][i] * (*phi)[w][j];
2984  }
2985  value[ dim * j + d2 ] *= absDetB;
2986 
2987  if (setZeros_ && std::fabs(value[ dim * j + d2 ]) < myeps_) {
2988  value[ dim * j + d2 ] = 0.;
2989  }
2990  }
2991  }
2992  for (UN j=0; j < phi->at(0).size(); j++){
2993  for (UN d2=0; d2<dim; d2++){
2994  indices[ dim * j + d2 ] = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) ) + d2 );
2995  }
2996  }
2997 
2998  GO row = GO ( dim * map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) ) + d1 );
2999  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
3000  }
3001  }
3002  }
3003  if (callFillComplete)
3004  A->fillComplete();
3005 }

3228 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
3229 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyBDStabilization(int dim,
3230  std::string FEType,
3231  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
3232  bool callFillComplete){
3233 
3234  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType != "P1",std::logic_error, "Only implemented for P1. Q1 is equivalent but we need to adjust scaling for the reference element.");
3235  UN FEloc = checkFE(dim,FEType);
3236 
3237  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
3238 
3239  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
3240 
3241  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
3242 
3243  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
3244 
3245  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
3246 
3247  UN deg = determineDegree(dim,FEType,FEType,Std,Std);
3248 
3249  getPhi( phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg );
3250 
3251  SC detB;
3252  SC absDetB;
3253  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
3254  GO glob_i, glob_j;
3255  vec_dbl_Type v_i(dim);
3256  vec_dbl_Type v_j(dim);
3257 
3258  SC refElementSize;
3259  SC refElementScale;
3260  if (dim==2) {
3261  refElementSize = 0.5;
3262  refElementScale = 1./9.;
3263  }
3264  else if(dim==3){
3265  refElementSize = 1./6.;
3266  refElementScale = 1./16.;
3267  }
3268  else
3269  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(true, std::logic_error, "Only implemented for 2D and 3D.");
3270 
3271  for (UN T=0; T<elements->numberElements(); T++) {
3272 
3273  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
3274  detB = B.computeDet( );
3275  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3276 
3277  for (UN i=0; i < phi->at(0).size(); i++) {
3278  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( phi->at(0).size(), 0. );
3279  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( phi->at(0).size(), 0 );
3280  for (UN j=0; j < value.size(); j++) {
3281  for (UN w=0; w<phi->size(); w++) {
3282  value[j] += weights->at(w) * (*phi)[w][i] * (*phi)[w][j];
3283  }
3284  value[j] *= absDetB;
3285  value[j] -= refElementSize * absDetB * refElementScale;
3286 
3287  indices[j] = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(j) );
3288  }
3289 
3290  GO row = map->getGlobalElement( elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) );
3291  A->insertGlobalValues( row, indices(), value() );
3292  }
3293 
3294  }
3295 
3296  if (callFillComplete)
3297  A->fillComplete();
3298 }

3302 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
3303 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLaplaceXDim(int dim,
3304  std::string FEType,
3305  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
3306  CoeffFuncDbl_Type func,
3307  double* parameters,
3308  bool callFillComplete)
3309 {
3310  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
3311  int FEloc = this->checkFE(dim,FEType);
3312 
3313  DomainConstPtr_Type domain = domainVec_.at(FEloc);
3314  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domain->getElementsC();
3315  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domain->getPointsRepeated();
3316  MapConstPtr_Type map = domain->getMapRepeated();
3317 
3318  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
3319  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weightsDPhi = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
3320  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type quadPts;
3321 
3322  // double val, value1_j, value2_j , value1_i, value2_i;
3323 
3324  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Grad);
3325 
3326  this->getDPhi(dPhi, weightsDPhi, dim, FEType, deg);
3327  getQuadratureValues(dim, deg, quadPts, weightsDPhi, FEType);
3328 
3329  // SC = double, GO = long, UN = int
3330  SC detB;
3331  SC absDetB;
3332  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
3333  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
3334  GO glob_i, glob_j;
3335 
3336 
3337  vec_dbl_ptr_Type dist = domain->getDistancesToInterface();
3338  if (dim == 2)
3339  {
3340  double val, value1_j, value2_j , value1_i, value2_i;
3341  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0);
3342 
3343  double distance1, distance2, distance3;
3344  vec_dbl_Type distance_mean(1); // Durchschnittliche Distanz des elements T
3345  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
3346  {
3347  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3348  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3349  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3350 
3351  distance1 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3352  distance2 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3353  distance3 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3354 
3355  distance_mean.at(0) = (distance1 + distance2 + distance3)/3.0; // Mittelwert
3356  double funcvalue = func(&distance_mean.at(0),parameters);
3357 
3358  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
3359  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
3360  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3361 
3362  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
3363  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
3364  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
3365 
3366  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
3367  {
3368  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( 1, 0. );
3369  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
3370 
3371  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
3372  {
3373  val = 0.0;
3374  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
3375  {
3376 
3377  value1_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(0);
3378  value2_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(1);
3379 
3380  value1_i = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i).at(0);
3381  value2_i = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i).at(1);
3382 
3383  val = val + funcvalue * weightsDPhi->at(k) * ( value1_j*value1_i + value2_j*value2_i );
3384  }
3385  val = absDetB * val;
3386  value[0] = val;
3387 
3388  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
3389  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
3390  indices[0] = glob_j;
3391 
3392 
3393  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value());
3394  glob_j++;
3395  indices[0] = glob_j;
3396  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value());
3397  }
3398  }
3399  }
3400  if (callFillComplete)
3401  {
3402  A->fillComplete();
3403  }
3404  }
3405  else if(dim == 3)
3406  {
3407  double val, value1_j, value2_j ,value3_j, value1_i, value2_i ,value3_i;
3408 
3409  long long glob_i, glob_j;
3410  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0), p4(3,0.0);
3411 
3412  double distance1, distance2, distance3, distance4;
3413  vec_dbl_Type distance_mean(1); // Durchschnittliche Distanz des elements T
3414  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
3415  {
3416  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3417  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3418  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3419  p4 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
3420

3422  distance2 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3423  distance3 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3424  distance4 = dist->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
3425 
3426  distance_mean.at(0) = (distance1 + distance2 + distance3 + distance4)/4.0; //Mittelwert
3427  double funcvalue = func(&distance_mean.at(0),parameters);
3428 
3429  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
3430  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
3431  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3432 
3433  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
3434  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
3435  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
3436 
3437  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
3438  {
3439  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( 1, 0. );
3440  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
3441 
3442  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
3443  {
3444  val = 0.0;
3445  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
3446  {
3447  value1_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(0);
3448  value2_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(1);
3449  value3_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(2);

3453  value3_i = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i).at(2);
3454

3456  }
3457  val = absDetB * val;
3458  value[0] = val;
3459

3461  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
3462  indices[0] = glob_j;
3463  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value());
3464  glob_j++;
3465  indices[0] = glob_j;
3466  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value());
3467  glob_j++;
3468  indices[0] = glob_j;
3469  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value());
3470 
3471  }
3472  }
3473  }
3474  if (callFillComplete)
3475  {
3476  A->fillComplete();
3477  }
3478  }

3484 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
3485 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyStress(int dim,
3486  std::string FEType,
3487  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
3488  CoeffFunc_Type func,
3489  int* parameters,
3490  bool callFillComplete)
3491 {
3492  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
3493  int FEloc = this->checkFE(dim,FEType);
3494 
3495  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
3496  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
3497  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
3498 
3499  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
3500  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weightsDPhi = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
3501  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type quadPts;
3502 
3503  // double value, value1_j, value2_j , value1_i, value2_i;
3504 
3505  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Grad);
3506  this->getDPhi(dPhi, weightsDPhi, dim, FEType, deg);
3507  getQuadratureValues(dim, deg, quadPts, weightsDPhi,FEType);
3508 
3509  // SC = double, GO = long, UN = int
3510  SC detB;
3511  SC absDetB;
3512  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
3513  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
3514  GO glob_i, glob_j;
3515 
3516  if (dim == 2)
3517  {
3518  double v11, v12, v21, v22, value1_j, value2_j , value1_i, value2_i;
3519  double e_11_j_1,e_12_j_1,e_21_j_1,e_22_j_1;
3520  double e_11_j_2,e_12_j_2,e_21_j_2,e_22_j_2;

3522  double e_11_i_2,e_12_i_2,e_21_i_2,e_22_i_2;
3523

3525  SmallMatrix<double> tmpRes2(dim);
3526  SmallMatrix<double> e1i(dim);
3527  SmallMatrix<double> e2i(dim);
3528  SmallMatrix<double> e1j(dim);
3529  SmallMatrix<double> e2j(dim);
3530 
3531  long long glob_i, glob_j;
3532  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0);
3533 
3534  vec_dbl_Type xy(2);
3535  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
3536  {
3537  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3538  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3539  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3540 
3541  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B, FEType);
3542  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
3543  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3544 
3545  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also B^(-T) * \grad_phi bzw. \grad_phi^T * B^(-1)
3546  // Also \hat{grad_phi}.
3547  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
3548  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
3549 
3550  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
3551  {
3552  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. );
3553  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. );
3554  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. );
3555  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. );
3556  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
3557 
3558  for (int j=0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
3559  {
3560  v11 = 0.0;v12 = 0.0;v21 = 0.0;v22 = 0.0;
3561  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
3562  {
3563  // Mappen der Gausspunkte (definiert auf T_ref) auf T (bzw. \Omega)
3564  // xy = F(quadPts) = B*quadPts + b, mit b = p1 (affin lineare Transformation)
3565  xy[0]=0.; xy[1]=0.;
3566  for (int r=0; r<2; r++) {
3567  xy[0] += B[0][r]*quadPts->at(k).at(r);
3568  xy[1] += B[1][r]*quadPts->at(k).at(r);
3569  }
3570  xy[0] += p1[0];
3571  xy[1] += p1[1];
3572 
3573  value1_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(0);
3574  value2_j = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j).at(1);
3575

3577  value2_i = dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i).at(1);
3578 
3579  tmpRes1[0][0] = value1_j;
3580  tmpRes1[0][1] = value2_j;
3581  tmpRes1[1][0] = 0.;
3582  tmpRes1[1][1] = 0.;
3583

3585  tmpRes2[0][1] = 0.;
3586  tmpRes2[1][0] = value2_j;
3587  tmpRes2[1][1] = 0.;
3588 
3589  tmpRes1.add(tmpRes2,e1j/*result*/);
3590

3592  e1i[0][1] = value2_i;
3593 
3594 
3595  tmpRes1[0][0] = 0.;
3596  tmpRes1[0][1] = 0.;
3597  tmpRes1[1][0] = value1_j;
3598  tmpRes1[1][1] = value2_j;
3599 
3600  tmpRes2[0][0] = 0.;
3601  tmpRes2[0][1] = value1_j;
3602  tmpRes2[1][0] = 0.;
3603  tmpRes2[1][1] = value2_j;
3604 
3605  tmpRes1.add(tmpRes2,e2j/*result*/);
3606

3608  e2i[1][1] = value2_i;
3609 
3610  double funcvalue = func(&xy.at(0),parameters);
3611  v11 = v11 + funcvalue * weightsDPhi->at(k) * e1i.innerProduct(e1j);
3612  v12 = v12 + funcvalue * weightsDPhi->at(k) * e1i.innerProduct(e2j);
3613  v21 = v21 + funcvalue * weightsDPhi->at(k) * e2i.innerProduct(e1j);
3614  v22 = v22 + funcvalue * weightsDPhi->at(k) * e2i.innerProduct(e2j);
3615 
3616  }
3617 
3618  v11 = absDetB * v11;
3619  v12 = absDetB * v12;
3620  v21 = absDetB * v21;
3621  v22 = absDetB * v22;
3622 
3623  value11[0] = v11;
3624  value12[0] = v12;
3625  value21[0] = v21;
3626  value22[0] = v22;
3627 
3628  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
3629  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
3630  indices[0] = glob_j;
3631 
3632  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11());
3633  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21());
3634  glob_j++;
3635  indices[0] = glob_j;
3636  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12());
3637  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22());
3638  }
3639  }
3640  }
3641  if (callFillComplete)
3642  {

3644  }
3645  }
3646  else if(dim == 3)

3649

3776  value12[0] = v12;
3777  value13[0] = v13;
3778  value21[0] = v21;
3779  value22[0] = v22;
3780  value23[0] = v23;

3782  value32[0] = v32;
3783  value33[0] = v33;

3786  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
3787  indices[0] = glob_j;
3788  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11());
3789  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21());
3790  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value31());
3791 
3792  glob_j++;
3793  indices[0] = glob_j;
3794  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12());
3795  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22());
3796  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value32());
3797 
3798  glob_j++;
3799  indices[0] = glob_j;
3800  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value13());
3801  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value23());
3802  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value33());
3803  }
3804  }
3805  }
3806  if (callFillComplete)
3807  {
3808  A->fillComplete();
3809  }
3810  }
