3816 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
3817 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyLinElasXDim(int dim,
3818  std::string FEType,
3819  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
3820  double lambda,
3821  double mu,
3822  bool callFillComplete)
3823 {
3824  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
3825  int FEloc = this->checkFE(dim,FEType);
3826 
3827  // Hole Elemente und Knotenliste
3828  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getElementsC();
3829  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getPointsRepeated();
3830  MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
3831 
3832  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
3833  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weightsDPhi = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
3834  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type quadPts;
3835 
3836  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Grad, Grad);
3837 
3838  // Hole die grad_phi, hier DPhi
3839  this->getDPhi(dPhi, weightsDPhi, dim, FEType, deg);
3840  getQuadratureValues(dim, deg, quadPts, weightsDPhi,FEType);
3841 
3842  // Definiere die Basisfunktion \phi_i bzw. \phi_j
3843  // vec_dbl_Type basisValues_i(dim,0.), basisValues_j(dim,0.);
3844 
3845  // SC = double, GO = long, UN = int
3846  SC detB;
3847  SC absDetB;
3848  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
3849  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
3850  GO glob_i, glob_j;
3851 
3852  // Fuer Zwischenergebniss
3853  SC res;
3854 
3855  // Fuer die Berechnung der Spur
3856  double res_trace_i, res_trace_j;
3857 
3858  if (dim == 2)
3859  {
3860 
3861  double v11, v12, v21, v22;
3862  // Setzte Vektoren der Groesse 2 und initialisiere mit 0.0 (double)
3863  vec_dbl_Type p1(2,0.0), p2(2,0.0), p3(2,0.0);
3864 
3865  // Matrizen der Groesse (2x2) in denen die einzelnen Epsilon-Tensoren berechnet werden.
3866  // Siehe unten fuer mehr.
3867  SmallMatrix<double> epsilonValuesMat1_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_i(dim),
3868  epsilonValuesMat1_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_j(dim);
3869 
3870  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
3871  {
3872  // Hole die Eckknoten des Dreiecks
3873  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3874  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3875  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3876 
3877  // Berechne die Transormationsmatrix B fuer das jeweilige Element (2D)
3878  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
3879  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
3880  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3881 
3882  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also B^(-T) * \grad_phi bzw. \grad_phi^T * B^(-1).
3883  // Also \hat{grad_phi}.
3884  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
3885  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
3886 
3887  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
3888  {
3889  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. );
3890  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. );
3891  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. );
3892  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. );
3893  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
3894 
3895  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
3896  {
3897  v11 = 0.0; v12 = 0.0; v21 = 0.0; v22 = 0.0;
3898  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
3899  {
3900  // In epsilonValuesMat1_i (2x2 Matrix) steht fuer die Ansatzfunktion i bzw. \phi_i
3901  // der epsilonTensor fuer eine skalare Ansatzfunktion fuer die Richtung 1 (vgl. Mat1).
3902  // Also in Mat1_i wird dann also phi_i = (phi_scalar_i, 0) gesetzt und davon \eps berechnet.
3903 
3904  // Stelle \hat{grad_phi_i} = basisValues_i auf, also B^(-T)*grad_phi_i
3905  // GradPhiOnRef( dPhi->at(k).at(i), b_T_inv, basisValues_i );
3906 
3907  // \eps(v) = \eps(phi_i)
3908  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat1_i, 0); // x-Richtung
3909  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat2_i, 1); // y-Richtung
3910 
3911  // Siehe oben, nur fuer j
3912  // GradPhiOnRef( DPhi->at(k).at(j), b_T_inv, basisValues_j );
3913 
3914  // \eps(u) = \eps(phi_j)
3915  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat1_j, 0); // x-Richtung
3916  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat2_j, 1); // y-Richtung
3917 
3918  // Nun berechnen wir \eps(u):\eps(v) = \eps(phi_j):\eps(phi_i).
3919  // Das Ergebniss steht in res.
3920  // Berechne zudem noch die Spur der Epsilon-Tensoren tr(\eps(u)) (j) und tr(\eps(v)) (i)
3921  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // x-x
3922  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
3923  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
3924  v11 = v11 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
3925 
3926  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // x-y
3927  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
3928  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
3929  v12 = v12 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
3930 
3931  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // y-x
3932  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
3933  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
3934  v21 = v21 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
3935 
3936  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // y-y
3937  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
3938  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
3939  v22 = v22 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
3940 
3941 
3942  }
3943  // Noch mit der abs(det(B)) skalieren
3944  v11 = absDetB * v11;
3945  v12 = absDetB * v12;
3946  v21 = absDetB * v21;
3947  v22 = absDetB * v22;
3948 
3949  value11[0] = v11;
3950  value12[0] = v12;
3951  value21[0] = v21;
3952  value22[0] = v22;
3953 
3954  // Hole die globale Zeile und Spalte in der die Eintraege hingeschrieben werden sollen
3955  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
3956  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
3957  indices[0] = glob_j;
3958  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11()); // x-x
3959  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21()); // y-x
3960  glob_j++;
3961  indices[0] = glob_j;
3962  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12()); // x-y
3963  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22()); // y-y
3964  }
3965  }
3966  }
3967  if (callFillComplete)
3968  {
3969  A->fillComplete();
3970  }
3971  }
3972  else if(dim == 3)
3973  {
3974 
3975  double v11, v12, v13, v21, v22, v23, v31, v32, v33;
3976 
3977  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0), p4(3,0.0);
3978  SmallMatrix<double> epsilonValuesMat1_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat3_i(dim),
3979  epsilonValuesMat1_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat3_j(dim);
3980 
3981  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
3982  {
3983  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
3984  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
3985  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
3986  p4 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
3987 
3988  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
3989  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
3990  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
3991 
3992  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
3993  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
3994  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
3995 
3996  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
3997  {
3998  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. );
3999  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. );
4000  Teuchos::Array<SC> value13( 1, 0. );
4001  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. );
4002  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. );

4004  Teuchos::Array<SC> value31( 1, 0. );
4005  Teuchos::Array<SC> value32( 1, 0. );
4006  Teuchos::Array<SC> value33( 1, 0. );
4007  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4008

4010  {

4012  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
4013  {

4015  // GradPhiOnRef( DPhi->at(k).at(i), b_T_inv, basisValues_i );
4016

4019  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat3_i, 2); // z-Richtung
4020

4124

4126 
4127  int dim = domain->getDimension();
4128  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domain->getPointsRepeated();
4129 
4130  //MapConstPtr_Type map = domainVec_.at(FEloc)->getMapRepeated();
4131 
4132  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
4133  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
4134

4136 
4137  getPhi( phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg );
4138

4147

4149  double E1 = params->sublist("Parameter Solid").get("E1",3.0e+5);

4156

4158  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4159  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);*/

4176  if(eModVecA[T] < eModMin)
4177  eModMin = eModVecA[T];
4178  }
4179  Teuchos::reduceAll<int, double> (*(domain->getComm()), Teuchos::REDUCE_MIN, eModMin, Teuchos::outArg (eModMin));
4180  Teuchos::reduceAll<int, double> (*(domain->getComm()), Teuchos::REDUCE_MAX, eModMax, Teuchos::outArg (eModMax));

4183  cout << " ################# eMOD Min: " << eModMin << " \t eModMax: " << eModMax<< " ############# " <<endl;
4184 
4185 
4186 }

4241  vec_dbl_Type p1(2,0.0), p2(2,0.0), p3(2,0.0);
4242 
4243  // Matrizen der Groesse (2x2) in denen die einzelnen Epsilon-Tensoren berechnet werden.
4244  // Siehe unten fuer mehr.
4245  SmallMatrix<double> epsilonValuesMat1_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_i(dim),
4246  epsilonValuesMat1_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_j(dim);
4247 
4248  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
4249  {
4251  lambda = E[T]* nu / ((1.+nu)*(1.-2.*nu));
4252  mu = E[T] / (2.*(1.+nu));
4253 
4254  // Hole die Eckknoten des Dreiecks
4255  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
4256  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
4257  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
4258 
4259  // Berechne die Transormationsmatrix B fuer das jeweilige Element (2D)
4260  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
4261  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4262  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
4263 
4264  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also B^(-T) * \grad_phi bzw. \grad_phi^T * B^(-1).
4265  // Also \hat{grad_phi}.
4266  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
4267  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
4268 
4269  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
4270  {
4271  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. );
4272  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. );
4273  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. );
4274  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. );
4275  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4276 
4277  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
4278  {
4279  v11 = 0.0; v12 = 0.0; v21 = 0.0; v22 = 0.0;
4280  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
4281  {
4282  // In epsilonValuesMat1_i (2x2 Matrix) steht fuer die Ansatzfunktion i bzw. \phi_i
4283  // der epsilonTensor fuer eine skalare Ansatzfunktion fuer die Richtung 1 (vgl. Mat1).
4284  // Also in Mat1_i wird dann also phi_i = (phi_scalar_i, 0) gesetzt und davon \eps berechnet.
4285 
4286  // Stelle \hat{grad_phi_i} = basisValues_i auf, also B^(-T)*grad_phi_i
4287  // GradPhiOnRef( dPhi->at(k).at(i), b_T_inv, basisValues_i );
4288 
4289  // \eps(v) = \eps(phi_i)
4290  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat1_i, 0); // x-Richtung
4291  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat2_i, 1); // y-Richtung
4292 
4293  // Siehe oben, nur fuer j
4294  // GradPhiOnRef( DPhi->at(k).at(j), b_T_inv, basisValues_j );
4295 
4296  // \eps(u) = \eps(phi_j)
4297  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat1_j, 0); // x-Richtung
4298  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat2_j, 1); // y-Richtung
4299 
4300  // Nun berechnen wir \eps(u):\eps(v) = \eps(phi_j):\eps(phi_i).
4301  // Das Ergebniss steht in res.
4302  // Berechne zudem noch die Spur der Epsilon-Tensoren tr(\eps(u)) (j) und tr(\eps(v)) (i)
4303  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // x-x
4304  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4305  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4306  v11 = v11 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4307 
4308  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // x-y
4309  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4310  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4311  v12 = v12 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4312 
4313  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // y-x
4314  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4315  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4316  v21 = v21 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4317 
4318  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // y-y
4319  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4320  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4321  v22 = v22 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4322 
4323 
4324  }
4325  // Noch mit der abs(det(B)) skalieren
4326  v11 = absDetB * v11;
4327  v12 = absDetB * v12;
4328  v21 = absDetB * v21;
4329  v22 = absDetB * v22;
4330 
4331  value11[0] = v11;
4332  value12[0] = v12;
4333  value21[0] = v21;
4334  value22[0] = v22;
4335 
4336  // Hole die globale Zeile und Spalte in der die Eintraege hingeschrieben werden sollen
4337  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
4338  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
4339  indices[0] = glob_j;
4340  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11()); // x-x
4341  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21()); // y-x
4342  glob_j++;
4343  indices[0] = glob_j;
4344  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12()); // x-y
4345  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22()); // y-y
4346  }
4347  }
4348  }
4349  if (callFillComplete)
4350  {
4351  A->fillComplete();
4352  }
4353  }
4354  else if(dim == 3)
4355  {
4356 
4357  double v11, v12, v13, v21, v22, v23, v31, v32, v33;
4358 
4359  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0), p4(3,0.0);
4360  SmallMatrix<double> epsilonValuesMat1_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_i(dim), epsilonValuesMat3_i(dim),
4361  epsilonValuesMat1_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat2_j(dim), epsilonValuesMat3_j(dim);
4362 
4363  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
4364  {
4365  lambda = E[T]* nu / ((1.+nu)*(1.-2.*nu));
4366  mu = E[T] / (2.*(1.+nu));
4367 
4368  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
4369  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
4370  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
4371  p4 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
4372 
4373  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
4374  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4375  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
4376 
4377  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
4378  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
4379  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
4380 
4381  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
4382  {
4383 
4384  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. );
4385  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. );
4386  Teuchos::Array<SC> value13( 1, 0. );
4387  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. );
4388  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. );
4389  Teuchos::Array<SC> value23( 1, 0. );
4390  Teuchos::Array<SC> value31( 1, 0. );
4391  Teuchos::Array<SC> value32( 1, 0. );
4392  Teuchos::Array<SC> value33( 1, 0. );
4393  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4394 
4395  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
4396  {
4397  v11 = 0.0; v12 = 0.0; v13 = 0.0; v21 = 0.0; v22 = 0.0; v23 = 0.0; v31 = 0.0; v32 = 0.0; v33 = 0.0;
4398  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
4399  {
4400 
4401  // GradPhiOnRef( DPhi->at(k).at(i), b_T_inv, basisValues_i );
4402 
4403  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat1_i, 0); // x-Richtung
4404  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat2_i, 1); // y-Richtung
4405  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(i), epsilonValuesMat3_i, 2); // z-Richtung
4406 
4407 
4408  // GradPhiOnRef( DPhi->at(k).at(j), b_T_inv, basisValues_j );
4409 
4410  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat1_j, 0); // x-Richtung
4411  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat2_j, 1); // y-Richtung
4412  epsilonTensor( dPhiTrans.at(k).at(j), epsilonValuesMat3_j, 2); // z-Richtung
4413 
4414  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // x-x
4415  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4416  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4417  v11 = v11 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4418 
4419  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // x-y
4420  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4421  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4422  v12 = v12 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4423 
4424  epsilonValuesMat1_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat3_j, res); // x-z
4425  epsilonValuesMat1_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4426  epsilonValuesMat3_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4427  v13 = v13 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4428 
4429  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // y-x
4430  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4431  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4432  v21 = v21 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4433 
4434  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // y-y
4435  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4436  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4437  v22 = v22 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4438 
4439  epsilonValuesMat2_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat3_j, res); // y-z
4440  epsilonValuesMat2_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4441  epsilonValuesMat3_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4442  v23 = v23 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4443 
4444  epsilonValuesMat3_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat1_j, res); // z-x
4445  epsilonValuesMat3_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4446  epsilonValuesMat1_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4447  v31 = v31 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4448 
4449  epsilonValuesMat3_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat2_j, res); // z-y
4450  epsilonValuesMat3_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4451  epsilonValuesMat2_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4452  v32 = v32 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4453 
4454  epsilonValuesMat3_i.innerProduct(epsilonValuesMat3_j, res); // z-z
4455  epsilonValuesMat3_i.trace(res_trace_i);
4456  epsilonValuesMat3_j.trace(res_trace_j);
4457  v33 = v33 + weightsDPhi->at(k)*(2*mu*res + lambda*res_trace_j*res_trace_i);
4458 
4459  }
4460  v11 = absDetB * v11;
4461  v12 = absDetB * v12;
4462  v13 = absDetB * v13;
4463  v21 = absDetB * v21;
4464  v22 = absDetB * v22;
4465  v23 = absDetB * v23;
4466  v31 = absDetB * v31;
4467  v32 = absDetB * v32;
4468  v33 = absDetB * v33;
4469 
4470  value11[0] = v11;
4471  value12[0] = v12;
4472  value13[0] = v13;
4473  value21[0] = v21;
4474  value22[0] = v22;
4475  value23[0] = v23;
4476  value31[0] = v31;
4477  value32[0] = v32;
4478  value33[0] = v33;
4479 
4480  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
4481  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
4482  indices[0] = glob_j;
4483  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11()); // x-x
4484  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21()); // y-x
4485  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value31()); // z-x
4486  glob_j++;
4487  indices[0] = glob_j;
4488  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12()); // x-y
4489  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22()); // y-y
4490  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value32()); // z-y
4491  glob_j++;
4492  indices[0] = glob_j;
4493  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value13()); // x-z
4494  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value23()); // y-z
4495  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value33()); // z-z
4496  }
4497  }
4498  }
4499  if (callFillComplete)
4500  {
4501  A->fillComplete();
4502  }
4503  }
4504 }

4506 
4507 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
4508 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyAdditionalConvection(int dim,
4509  std::string FEType,
4510  MatrixPtr_Type &A,
4511  MultiVectorPtr_Type w,
4512  bool callFillComplete)
4513 {
4514 
4515  TEUCHOS_TEST_FOR_EXCEPTION(FEType == "P0",std::logic_error, "Not implemented for P0");
4516  int FEloc = this->checkFE(dim,FEType);
4517 
4518  DomainConstPtr_Type domain = domainVec_.at(FEloc);
4519  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domain->getElementsC();
4520  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domain->getPointsRepeated();
4521  MapConstPtr_Type map = domain->getMapRepeated();
4522 
4523  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhi;
4524  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phi;
4525  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
4526  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type quadPts;
4527 
4528  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, Grad); // Fuer diskretes (\grad \cdot w) in den Gausspuntken
4529  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType, FEType, Std, Std, extraDeg);
4530 
4531  this->getDPhi(dPhi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
4532  this->getPhi(phi, weights, dim, FEType, deg);
4533  getQuadratureValues(dim, deg, quadPts, weights,FEType);
4534 
4535  // SC = double, GO = long, UN = int
4536  SC detB;
4537  SC absDetB;
4538  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
4539  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
4540  GO glob_i, glob_j;
4541 
4542  // Der nichtlineare Teil als Array
4543  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > wArray = w->getData(0);
4544 
4545  if (dim == 2)
4546  {
4547  double val;
4548  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0);
4549 
4550  vec2D_dbl_Type w11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.)); // diskretes w_11. Siehe unten.
4551  vec2D_dbl_Type w22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4552  vec2D_dbl_Type divergenz(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4553 
4554  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
4555  {
4556  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
4557  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
4558  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
4559 
4560  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
4561  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4562  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
4563 
4564  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
4565  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
4566  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
4567 
4568  // Diskretes \div(w) = (\grad \cdot w) = w_11 + w_22 berechnen,
4569  // wobei w_ij = \frac{\partial w_i}{\partial x_j} ist.
4570  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTrans.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4571  {
4572  w11[0][k] = 0.0;
4573  w22[0][k] = 0.0;
4574  for(int i = 0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++)
4575  {
4576  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
4577  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
4578  w11[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTrans[k][i][0];
4579  w22[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTrans[k][i][1];
4580 
4581  // TEST
4582  // LO indexTest1 = dim * i + 0;
4583  // LO indexTest2 = dim * i + 1;
4584  // w11[0][k] += wTest[indexTest1] * dPhiTrans[k][i][0];
4585  // w22[0][k] += wTest[indexTest2] * dPhiTrans[k][i][1];
4586  }
4587  }
4588 
4589  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTrans.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4590  {
4591  divergenz[0][k] = w11[0][k] + w22[0][k];
4592  // if(T == 0)
4593  // {
4594  // std::cout << "k: " << k << " Divergenz: " << divergenz[0][k] << '\n';
4595  // }
4596  }
4597 
4598 
4599  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
4600  {
4601  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( 1, 0. );
4602  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4603 
4604  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
4605  {
4606  val = 0.0;
4607  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
4608  {
4609  val = val + divergenz[0][k] * weights->at(k) * (*phi)[k][i] * (*phi)[k][j];
4610  }
4611  val = absDetB * val;
4612  value[0] = val;
4613 
4614  // if(T == 0)
4615  // {
4616  // std::cout << "i: " << i << " j: " << j << " val: " << val << '\n';
4617  // }
4618 
4619  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
4620  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
4621  indices[0] = glob_j;
4622 
4623  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value());
4624  glob_j++;
4625  indices[0] = glob_j;
4626  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value());
4627  }
4628  }
4629  }
4630  if (callFillComplete)
4631  {
4632  A->fillComplete();
4633  }
4634  }
4635  else if(dim == 3)
4636  {
4637  double val;
4638 
4639  // long long glob_i, glob_j;
4640  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0), p4(3,0.0);
4641 
4642  vec2D_dbl_Type w11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.)); // diskretes w_11. Siehe unten.
4643  vec2D_dbl_Type w22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4644  vec2D_dbl_Type w33(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4645  vec2D_dbl_Type divergenz(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4646 
4647  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
4648  {
4649  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
4650  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
4651  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
4652  p4 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
4653 
4654  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
4655  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4656  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
4657 
4658  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
4659  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTrans( dPhi->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhi->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
4660  applyBTinv( dPhi, dPhiTrans, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
4661 
4662  // Diskretes \div(w) = (\grad \cdot w) = w_11 + w_22 + w33 berechnen,
4663  // wobei w_ij = \frac{\partial w_i}{\partial x_j} ist.
4664  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTrans.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4665  {
4666  w11[0][k] = 0.0;
4667  w22[0][k] = 0.0;
4668  w33[0][k] = 0.0;
4669  for(int i = 0; i < dPhiTrans[0].size(); i++)
4670  {
4671  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
4672  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
4673  LO index3 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 2; // z
4674  w11[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTrans[k][i][0];
4675  w22[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTrans[k][i][1];
4676  w33[0][k] += wArray[index3] * dPhiTrans[k][i][2];
4677  }
4678  }
4679 
4680  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTrans.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4681  {
4682  divergenz[0][k] = w11[0][k] + w22[0][k] + w33[0][k];
4683  }
4684 
4685  for (int i = 0; i < dPhi->at(0).size(); i++)
4686  {
4687  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( 1, 0. );
4688  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4689 
4690  for (int j = 0; j < dPhi->at(0).size(); j++)
4691  {
4692  val = 0.0;
4693  for (int k = 0; k < dPhi->size(); k++)
4694  {
4695  val = val + divergenz[0][k] * weights->at(k) * (*phi)[k][i] * (*phi)[k][j];
4696  }
4697  val = absDetB * val;
4698  value[0] = val;
4699 
4700  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
4701  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
4702  indices[0] = glob_j;
4703  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value());
4704  glob_j++;
4705  indices[0] = glob_j;
4706  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value());
4707  glob_j++;
4708  indices[0] = glob_j;
4709  A->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value());
4710 
4711  }
4712  }
4713  }
4714  if (callFillComplete)
4715  {
4716  A->fillComplete();
4717  }
4718  }
4719 }

4721 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
4722 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyDummyCoupling(int dim,
4723  std::string FEType,
4724  MatrixPtr_Type &C,
4725  int FEloc, // 0 = Fluid, 2 = Struktur
4726  bool callFillComplete)
4727 {
4728  DomainConstPtr_Type domain = domainVec_.at(FEloc);
4729 
4730  MapConstPtr_Type mapInterfaceVecField = domain->getInterfaceMapVecFieldUnique(); // Interface-Map in der Interface-Nummerierung
4731  MapConstPtr_Type mapGlobalInterfaceVecField = domain->getGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldUnique(); // Interface-Map in der globalen Nummerierung
4732 
4733  MapConstPtr_Type mapFieldPartial = domain->getGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldPartial();
4734 
4735  Teuchos::Array<SC> value( 1, 0. );
4736  value[0] = 1.0; // da Einheitsmatrix
4737  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
4738 
4739  GO dofGlobal, dofLocal;
4740 
4741  for(int k = 0; k < mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getNodeNumElements(); k++)
4742  {
4743  dofGlobal = mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement(k);
4744  if ( mapFieldPartial->getLocalElement( dofGlobal ) == Teuchos::OrdinalTraits<LO>::invalid() ) {
4745  // Globale ID des Interface-Knotens bzgl. der Globalen oder Interface-Nummerierung
4746  dofGlobal = mapInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement( k );
4747  indices[0] = dofGlobal;
4748  C->insertGlobalValues(dofGlobal, indices(), value());
4749  }
4750  }
4751 
4752  if (callFillComplete)
4753  C->fillComplete(mapInterfaceVecField, mapInterfaceVecField);
4754 
4755 }

4757 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>

4759  std::string FEType,
4760  MatrixPtr_Type &C,
4761  MatrixPtr_Type &C_T,
4762  int FEloc1, // 0 = Fluid, 2 = Struktur
4763  int FEloc2, // 0 = Fluid, 2 = Struktur
4764  MapConstPtr_Type map1, // DomainMap: InterfaceMapVecFieldUnique = Spalten von C_T
4765  MapConstPtr_Type map2, // RangeMap: this->getDomain(0)->getMapVecFieldUnique() = Zeilen von C_T

4778  mapGlobalInterfaceVecField = domain1->getOtherGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldUnique();

4790  if (mapFieldPartial.is_null()) {
4791  for(int k = 0; k < mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getNodeNumElements(); k++)
4792  {
4793  // Globale ID des Interface-Knotens bzgl. der Globalen oder Interface-Nummerierung
4794  dofGlobal = mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement(k);
4795  dofLocal = mapInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement(k);
4796 
4797  indices[0] = dofLocal;
4798  C_T->insertGlobalValues(dofGlobal, indices(), value());
4799  indices[0] = dofGlobal;
4800  C->insertGlobalValues(dofLocal, indices(), value());
4801 
4802  }

4804  else{
4805  for(int k = 0; k < mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getNodeNumElements(); k++) {
4806  dofGlobal = mapGlobalInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement(k);
4807  if ( mapFieldPartial->getLocalElement( dofGlobal ) != Teuchos::OrdinalTraits<LO>::invalid() ) {
4808 
4809  dofLocal = mapInterfaceVecField->getGlobalElement(k);
4810 
4811  indices[0] = dofLocal;
4812  C_T->insertGlobalValues(dofGlobal, indices(), value());
4813  indices[0] = dofGlobal;
4814  C->insertGlobalValues(dofLocal, indices(), value());
4815  }
4816  }
4817  }
4818 
4819  if (callFillComplete)
4820  {
4821  // Erstes Argument: Domain (=Spalten von C_T)
4822  // Zweites Arguement: Range (=Zeilen von C_T)
4823  C_T->fillComplete(map1, map2);
4824  C->fillComplete(map2, map1);
4825  }

4829 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
4830 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyGeometryCoupling(int dim,
4831  std::string FEType,
4832  MatrixPtr_Type &C,
4833  int FEloc, // 0 = Fluid, 2 = Struktur, 4 = 0 = Geometrie

4836  MapConstPtr_Type map3, // RangeMap: this->getDomain(4)->getMapVecFieldUnique() = Zeilen von C

4843  MapConstPtr_Type mapOtherInt = domain->getOtherGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldUnique(); // Interface-Map in der globalen Nummerierung von other. For FELoc=0 or =4, otherInterface has solid dofs
4844  MapConstPtr_Type mapPartInt = domain->getGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldPartial();
4845  MapConstPtr_Type mapOtherPartInt = domain->getOtherGlobalInterfaceMapVecFieldPartial();

4851  if (mapPartInt.is_null()) {

4853  dofRow = mapInt->getGlobalElement(k);
4854  indices[0] = mapOtherInt->getGlobalElement(k);
4855  C->insertGlobalValues(dofRow, indices(), value());
4856  }
4857  }
4858  else{
4859  for(int k = 0; k < mapPartInt->getNodeNumElements(); k++){
4860  dofRow = mapPartInt->getGlobalElement(k);
4861  indices[0] = mapOtherPartInt->getGlobalElement(k);
4862  C->insertGlobalValues(dofRow, indices(), value());
4863  }
4864  }

4866  {
4867  // (Domain, Range)

4869  }
4870 }

4873 template <class SC, class LO, class GO, class NO>
4874 void FE<SC,LO,GO,NO>::assemblyShapeDerivativeVelocity(int dim,
4875  std::string FEType1, // P2
4876  std::string FEType2, // P1
4877  MatrixPtr_Type &D,
4878  int FEloc, // 0 = Fluid (Velocity)
4879  MultiVectorPtr_Type u, // Geschwindigkeit
4880  MultiVectorPtr_Type w, // Beschleunigung Gitter
4881  MultiVectorPtr_Type p, // Druck
4882  double dt, // Zeitschrittweite
4883  double rho, // Dichte vom Fluid
4884  double nu, // Viskositaet vom Fluid
4885  bool callFillComplete)
4886 {
4887  // int FEloc = this->checkFE(dim,FEType1);
4888 
4889  DomainConstPtr_Type domain = domainVec_.at(FEloc);
4890  ElementsPtr_Type elements = domain->getElementsC();
4891  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type pointsRep = domain->getPointsRepeated();
4892  MapConstPtr_Type map = domain->getMapRepeated();
4893 
4894  vec3D_dbl_ptr_Type dPhiU;
4895  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phiU;
4896  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type phiP;
4897  vec_dbl_ptr_Type weights = Teuchos::rcp(new vec_dbl_Type(0));
4898  vec2D_dbl_ptr_Type quadPts;
4899 
4900  // Hoechste Quadraturordnung angeben (= Zusaetzlicher Term wg. non-conservativ); bei P2/P1 hier Ordnung 6
4901  UN extraDeg = determineDegree( dim, FEType1, Grad) + determineDegree( dim, FEType1, Grad);
4902  UN deg = determineDegree( dim, FEType1, FEType1, Std, Std, extraDeg);
4903 
4904  this->getDPhi(dPhiU, weights, dim, FEType1, deg);
4905  this->getPhi(phiU, weights, dim, FEType1, deg);
4906  this->getPhi(phiP, weights, dim, FEType2, deg);
4907  getQuadratureValues(dim, deg, quadPts, weights,FEType1);
4908 
4909  // SC = double, GO = long, UN = int
4910  SC detB;
4911  SC absDetB;
4912  SmallMatrix<SC> B(dim);
4913  SmallMatrix<SC> Binv(dim);
4914  GO glob_i, glob_j;
4915 
4916  // Der nichtlineare Teil als Array
4917  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > uArray = u->getData(0);
4918  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > wArray = w->getData(0);
4919  Teuchos::ArrayRCP< const SC > pArray = p->getData(0);
4920 
4921  if (dim == 2)
4922  {
4923  double val11, val12, val21, val22;
4924  double valDK1_11, valDK1_12, valDK1_21, valDK1_22;
4925  double valDK2_11, valDK2_12, valDK2_21, valDK2_22;
4926  double valDN_11, valDN_12, valDN_21, valDN_22;
4927  double valDW_11, valDW_12, valDW_21, valDW_22;
4928  double valDP_11, valDP_12, valDP_21, valDP_22;
4929  double valDM_11, valDM_12, valDM_21, valDM_22;
4930  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0);
4931 
4932  // Alle diskreten Vektoren aufstellen, dabei bezeichnet Xij = X_ij,
4933  // also i-te Komponenten von X nach der j-ten Variablen abgeleitet.
4934  // Der Gradient ist bei mir wie folgt definiert: \grad(u) = [u11, u12; u21 u22] = [grad(u_1)^T; grad(u_2)^T]
4935  vec2D_dbl_Type u1Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4936  vec2D_dbl_Type u2Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4937  vec2D_dbl_Type w1Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4938  vec2D_dbl_Type w2Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4939  vec2D_dbl_Type pLoc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4940  vec2D_dbl_Type u11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4941  vec2D_dbl_Type u12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4942  vec2D_dbl_Type u21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4943  vec2D_dbl_Type u22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4944  vec2D_dbl_Type w11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4945  vec2D_dbl_Type w12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4946  vec2D_dbl_Type w21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4947  vec2D_dbl_Type w22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4948  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4949  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4950  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4951  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
4952 
4953  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
4954  {
4955  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
4956  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
4957  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
4958 
4959  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
4960  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
4961  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
4962 
4963  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
4964  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTransU( dPhiU->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhiU->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
4965  applyBTinv( dPhiU, dPhiTransU, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
4966 
4967  // Diskrete Vektoren u1, u2, w1 und w2 berechnen
4968  for(int k = 0; k < phiU->size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4969  {
4970  u1Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
4971  u2Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
4972  w1Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
4973  w2Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
4974  for(int i = 0; i < phiU->at(0).size(); i++)
4975  {
4976  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
4977  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
4978  u1Loc[0][k] += uArray[index1] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
4979  u2Loc[0][k] += uArray[index2] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
4980  w1Loc[0][k] += wArray[index1] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
4981  w2Loc[0][k] += wArray[index2] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
4982 
4983  }
4984  }
4985 
4986  // Diskreten Vektor p berechnen
4987  // Beachte: phiP->size() = phiU->size()
4988  for(int k = 0; k < phiP->size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
4989  {
4990  pLoc[0][k] = 0.0;
4991  for(int i = 0; i < phiP->at(0).size(); i++)
4992  {
4993  // Die ersten Eintraege in der Elementliste sind P1
4994  // Alternativ elements2 holen
4995  LO index = elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0;
4996  pLoc[0][k] += pArray[index] * phiP->at(k).at(i);
4997 
4998  }
4999  }
5000 
5001  // Diskrete Grad-Vektoren berechnen,
5002  // wobei z.B. w_ij = \frac{\partial w_i}{\partial x_j} ist.
5003  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTransU.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5004  {
5005  u11[0][k] = 0.0;
5006  u12[0][k] = 0.0;
5007  u21[0][k] = 0.0;
5008  u22[0][k] = 0.0;
5009  w11[0][k] = 0.0;
5010  w12[0][k] = 0.0;
5011  w21[0][k] = 0.0;
5012  w22[0][k] = 0.0;
5013  for(int i = 0; i < dPhiTransU[0].size(); i++)
5014  {
5015  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
5016  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
5017  u11[0][k] += uArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5018  u12[0][k] += uArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5019  u21[0][k] += uArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5020  u22[0][k] += uArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5021  w11[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5022  w12[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5023  w21[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5024  w22[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5025 
5026  }
5027  }
5028 
5029  // Diskretes \sigma = \rho * \nu * ( grad u + (grad u)^T ) - pI berechnen
5030  // Beachte: phiP->size() = phiU->size()
5031  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTransU.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5032  {
5033  sigma11[0][k] = rho * nu * (u11[0][k] + u11[0][k]) - pLoc[0][k];
5034  sigma12[0][k] = rho * nu * (u12[0][k] + u21[0][k]);
5035  sigma21[0][k] = rho * nu * (u21[0][k] + u12[0][k]);
5036  sigma22[0][k] = rho * nu * (u22[0][k] + u22[0][k]) - pLoc[0][k];
5037  }
5038 
5039 
5040  for (int i = 0; i < dPhiU->at(0).size(); i++)
5041  {
5042  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. ); // x-x
5043  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. ); // x-y
5044  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. ); // y-x
5045  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. ); // y-y
5046  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
5047 
5048  for (int j = 0; j < dPhiU->at(0).size(); j++)
5049  {
5050  // DK1
5051  valDK1_11 = 0.0;
5052  valDK1_12 = 0.0;
5053  valDK1_21 = 0.0;
5054  valDK1_22 = 0.0;
5055 
5056  // DK2
5057  valDK2_11 = 0.0;
5058  valDK2_12 = 0.0;
5059  valDK2_21 = 0.0;
5060  valDK2_22 = 0.0;
5061 
5062  // DN
5063  valDN_11 = 0.0;
5064  valDN_12 = 0.0;
5065  valDN_21 = 0.0;
5066  valDN_22 = 0.0;
5067 
5068  // DW
5069  valDW_11 = 0.0;
5070  valDW_12 = 0.0;
5071  valDW_21 = 0.0;
5072  valDW_22 = 0.0;
5073 
5074  // DP
5075  valDP_11 = 0.0;
5076  valDP_12 = 0.0;
5077  valDP_21 = 0.0;
5078  valDP_22 = 0.0;
5079 
5080  // DM
5081  valDM_11 = 0.0;
5082  valDM_12 = 0.0;
5083  valDM_21 = 0.0;
5084  valDM_22 = 0.0;
5085 
5086  for (int k = 0; k < dPhiU->size(); k++)
5087  {
5088  // DK1
5089  valDK1_11 = valDK1_11 + weights->at(k) *
5090  ( 2 * u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5091  u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5092  u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5093  valDK1_12 = valDK1_12 + weights->at(k) *
5094  ( 2 * u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5095  u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5096  u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5097  valDK1_21 = valDK1_21 + weights->at(k) *
5098  ( u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5099  u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5100  2 * u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5101  valDK1_22 = valDK1_22 + weights->at(k) *
5102  ( u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5103  u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5104  2 * u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5105 
5106  // DK2
5107  valDK2_11 = valDK2_11 + weights->at(k) *
5108  ( -sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5109  sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5110  valDK2_12 = valDK2_12 + weights->at(k) *
5111  ( sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5112  -sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5113  valDK2_21 = valDK2_21 + weights->at(k) *
5114  ( -sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5115  sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5116  valDK2_22 = valDK2_22 + weights->at(k) *
5117  ( sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5118  -sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] );
5119 
5120  // DN
5121  valDN_11 = valDN_11 + weights->at(k) *
5122  ( -(u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5123  (u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5124  valDN_12 = valDN_12 + weights->at(k) *
5125  ( (u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) -
5126  (u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5127  valDN_21 = valDN_21 + weights->at(k) *
5128  ( -(u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5129  (u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5130  valDN_22 = valDN_22 + weights->at(k) *
5131  ( (u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) -
5132  (u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k]) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5133 
5134  // DW
5135  valDW_11 = valDW_11 + weights->at(k) *
5136  ( u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5137  valDW_12 = valDW_12 + weights->at(k) *
5138  ( u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5139  valDW_21 = valDW_21 + weights->at(k) *
5140  ( u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5141  valDW_22 = valDW_22 + weights->at(k) *
5142  ( u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5143 
5144  // DP
5145  valDP_11 = valDP_11 + weights->at(k) *
5146  ( ( -w21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + w22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5147  valDP_12 = valDP_12 + weights->at(k) *
5148  ( ( w11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - w12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5149  valDP_21 = valDP_21 + weights->at(k) *
5150  ( ( -w21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + w22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5151  valDP_22 = valDP_22 + weights->at(k) *
5152  ( ( w11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - w12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5153 
5154  // DM
5155  valDM_11 = valDM_11 + weights->at(k) *
5156  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5157  valDM_12 = valDM_12 + weights->at(k) *
5158  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5159  valDM_21 = valDM_21 + weights->at(k) *
5160  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5161  valDM_22 = valDM_22 + weights->at(k) *
5162  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5163  }
5164 
5165  val11 = -rho*nu*valDK1_11 + valDK2_11 + rho*valDN_11 - rho*valDP_11 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_11 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_11;
5166  val12 = -rho*nu*valDK1_12 + valDK2_12 + rho*valDN_12 - rho*valDP_12 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_12 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_12;
5167  val21 = -rho*nu*valDK1_21 + valDK2_21 + rho*valDN_21 - rho*valDP_21 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_21 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_21;
5168  val22 = -rho*nu*valDK1_22 + valDK2_22 + rho*valDN_22 - rho*valDP_22 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_22 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_22;
5169 
5170  val11 = absDetB * val11;
5171  val12 = absDetB * val12;
5172  val21 = absDetB * val21;
5173  val22 = absDetB * val22;
5174 
5175  value11[0] = val11; // x-x
5176  value12[0] = val12; // x-y
5177  value21[0] = val21; // y-x
5178  value22[0] = val22; // y-y
5179 
5180  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
5181  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
5182  indices[0] = glob_j;
5183 
5184  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11()); // x-x
5185  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21()); // y-x
5186  glob_j++;
5187  indices[0] = glob_j;
5188  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12()); // x-y
5189  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22()); // y-y
5190  }
5191  }
5192  }
5193  if (callFillComplete)
5194  {
5195  D->fillComplete();
5196  }
5197  }
5198  else if(dim == 3)
5199  {
5200  double val11, val12, val13, val21, val22, val23, val31, val32, val33;
5201  double valDK1_11, valDK1_12, valDK1_13, valDK1_21, valDK1_22, valDK1_23, valDK1_31, valDK1_32, valDK1_33;
5202  double valDK2_11, valDK2_12, valDK2_13, valDK2_21, valDK2_22, valDK2_23, valDK2_31, valDK2_32, valDK2_33;
5203  double valDN_11, valDN_12, valDN_13, valDN_21, valDN_22, valDN_23, valDN_31, valDN_32, valDN_33;
5204  double valDW_11, valDW_12, valDW_13, valDW_21, valDW_22, valDW_23, valDW_31, valDW_32, valDW_33;
5205  double valDP_11, valDP_12, valDP_13, valDP_21, valDP_22, valDP_23, valDP_31, valDP_32, valDP_33;
5206  double valDM_11, valDM_12, valDM_13, valDM_21, valDM_22, valDM_23, valDM_31, valDM_32, valDM_33;
5207  vec_dbl_Type p1(3,0.0), p2(3,0.0), p3(3,0.0), p4(3,0.0);
5208 
5209  // Alle diskreten Vektoren aufstellen, dabei bezeichnet Xij = X_ij,
5210  // also i-te Komponenten von X nach der j-ten Variablen abgeleitet.
5211  // Der Gradient ist bei mir wie folgt definiert: \grad(u) = [u11, u12; u21 u22] = [grad(u_1)^T; grad(u_2)^T]
5212  vec2D_dbl_Type u1Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5213  vec2D_dbl_Type u2Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5214  vec2D_dbl_Type u3Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5215  vec2D_dbl_Type w1Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5216  vec2D_dbl_Type w2Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5217  vec2D_dbl_Type w3Loc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5218  vec2D_dbl_Type pLoc(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5219  vec2D_dbl_Type u11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5220  vec2D_dbl_Type u12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5221  vec2D_dbl_Type u13(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5222  vec2D_dbl_Type u21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5223  vec2D_dbl_Type u22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5224  vec2D_dbl_Type u23(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5225  vec2D_dbl_Type u31(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5226  vec2D_dbl_Type u32(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5227  vec2D_dbl_Type u33(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5228  vec2D_dbl_Type w11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5229  vec2D_dbl_Type w12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5230  vec2D_dbl_Type w13(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5231  vec2D_dbl_Type w21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5232  vec2D_dbl_Type w22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5233  vec2D_dbl_Type w23(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5234  vec2D_dbl_Type w31(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5235  vec2D_dbl_Type w32(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5236  vec2D_dbl_Type w33(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5237  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma11(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5238  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma12(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5239  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma13(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5240  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma21(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5241  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma22(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5242  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma23(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5243  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma31(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5244  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma32(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5245  vec2D_dbl_Type sigma33(1, vec_dbl_Type(weights->size(), -1.));
5246 
5247  for (int T = 0; T < elements->numberElements(); T++)
5248  {
5249  p1 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(0));
5250  p2 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(1));
5251  p3 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(2));
5252  p4 = pointsRep->at(elements->getElement(T).getNode(3));
5253 
5254  buildTransformation(elements->getElement(T).getVectorNodeList(), pointsRep, B);
5255  detB = B.computeInverse(Binv);
5256  absDetB = std::fabs(detB);
5257 
5258  // dPhiTrans sind die transformierten Basifunktionen, also \grad_phi * B^(-T)
5259  vec3D_dbl_Type dPhiTransU( dPhiU->size(), vec2D_dbl_Type( dPhiU->at(0).size(), vec_dbl_Type(dim,0.) ) );
5260  applyBTinv( dPhiU, dPhiTransU, Binv ); //dPhiTrans berechnen
5261 
5262  // Diskrete Vektoren u1, u2, w1 und w2 berechnen
5263  for(int k = 0; k < phiU->size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5264  {
5265  u1Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5266  u2Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5267  u3Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5268  w1Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5269  w2Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5270  w3Loc[0][k] = 0.0;
5271  for(int i = 0; i < phiU->at(0).size(); i++)
5272  {
5273  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
5274  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
5275  LO index3 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 2; // z
5276  u1Loc[0][k] += uArray[index1] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5277  u2Loc[0][k] += uArray[index2] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5278  u3Loc[0][k] += uArray[index3] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5279  w1Loc[0][k] += wArray[index1] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5280  w2Loc[0][k] += wArray[index2] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5281  w3Loc[0][k] += wArray[index3] * phiU->at(k).at(i);
5282  }
5283  }
5284 
5285  // Diskreten Vektor p berechnen
5286  // Beachte: phiP->size() = phiU->size()
5287  for(int k = 0; k < phiP->size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5288  {
5289  pLoc[0][k] = 0.0;
5290  for(int i = 0; i < phiP->at(0).size(); i++)
5291  {
5292  // Die ersten Eintraege in der Elementliste sind P1
5293  LO index = elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0;
5294  pLoc[0][k] += pArray[index] * phiP->at(k).at(i);
5295  }
5296  }
5297 
5298  // Diskrete Grad-Vektoren berechnen,
5299  // wobei z.B. w_ij = \frac{\partial w_i}{\partial x_j} ist.
5300  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTransU.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5301  {
5302  u11[0][k] = 0.0;
5303  u12[0][k] = 0.0;
5304  u13[0][k] = 0.0;
5305  u21[0][k] = 0.0;
5306  u22[0][k] = 0.0;
5307  u23[0][k] = 0.0;
5308  u31[0][k] = 0.0;
5309  u32[0][k] = 0.0;
5310  u33[0][k] = 0.0;
5311  w11[0][k] = 0.0;
5312  w12[0][k] = 0.0;
5313  w13[0][k] = 0.0;
5314  w21[0][k] = 0.0;
5315  w22[0][k] = 0.0;
5316  w23[0][k] = 0.0;
5317  w31[0][k] = 0.0;
5318  w32[0][k] = 0.0;
5319  w33[0][k] = 0.0;
5320  for(int i = 0; i < dPhiTransU[0].size(); i++)
5321  {
5322  LO index1 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 0; // x
5323  LO index2 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 1; // y
5324  LO index3 = dim * elements->getElement(T).getNode(i) + 2; // z
5325  u11[0][k] += uArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5326  u12[0][k] += uArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5327  u13[0][k] += uArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5328  u21[0][k] += uArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5329  u22[0][k] += uArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5330  u23[0][k] += uArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5331  u31[0][k] += uArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5332  u32[0][k] += uArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5333  u33[0][k] += uArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5334  w11[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5335  w12[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5336  w13[0][k] += wArray[index1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5337  w21[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5338  w22[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5339  w23[0][k] += wArray[index2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5340  w31[0][k] += wArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0];
5341  w32[0][k] += wArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1];
5342  w33[0][k] += wArray[index3] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5343  }
5344  }
5345 
5346  // Diskretes \sigma = \rho * \nu * ( grad u + (grad u)^T ) - pI berechnen
5347  // Beachte: phiP->size() = phiU->size()
5348  for(int k = 0; k < dPhiTransU.size(); k++) // Quadraturpunkte
5349  {
5350  sigma11[0][k] = rho * nu * (u11[0][k] + u11[0][k]) - pLoc[0][k];
5351  sigma12[0][k] = rho * nu * (u12[0][k] + u21[0][k]);
5352  sigma13[0][k] = rho * nu * (u13[0][k] + u31[0][k]);
5353  sigma21[0][k] = rho * nu * (u21[0][k] + u12[0][k]);
5354  sigma22[0][k] = rho * nu * (u22[0][k] + u22[0][k]) - pLoc[0][k];
5355  sigma23[0][k] = rho * nu * (u23[0][k] + u32[0][k]);
5356  sigma31[0][k] = rho * nu * (u31[0][k] + u13[0][k]);
5357  sigma32[0][k] = rho * nu * (u32[0][k] + u23[0][k]);
5358  sigma33[0][k] = rho * nu * (u33[0][k] + u33[0][k]) - pLoc[0][k];
5359  }
5360 
5361 
5362  for (int i = 0; i < dPhiU->at(0).size(); i++)
5363  {
5364  Teuchos::Array<SC> value11( 1, 0. ); // x-x
5365  Teuchos::Array<SC> value12( 1, 0. ); // x-y
5366  Teuchos::Array<SC> value13( 1, 0. ); // x-z
5367  Teuchos::Array<SC> value21( 1, 0. ); // y-x
5368  Teuchos::Array<SC> value22( 1, 0. ); // y-y
5369  Teuchos::Array<SC> value23( 1, 0. ); // y-z
5370  Teuchos::Array<SC> value31( 1, 0. ); // z-x
5371  Teuchos::Array<SC> value32( 1, 0. ); // z-y
5372  Teuchos::Array<SC> value33( 1, 0. ); // z-z
5373  Teuchos::Array<GO> indices( 1, 0 );
5374 
5375  for (int j = 0; j < dPhiU->at(0).size(); j++)
5376  {
5377  // DK1
5378  valDK1_11 = 0.0;
5379  valDK1_12 = 0.0;
5380  valDK1_13 = 0.0;
5381  valDK1_21 = 0.0;
5382  valDK1_22 = 0.0;
5383  valDK1_23 = 0.0;
5384  valDK1_31 = 0.0;
5385  valDK1_32 = 0.0;
5386  valDK1_33 = 0.0;
5387 
5388  // DK2
5389  valDK2_11 = 0.0;
5390  valDK2_12 = 0.0;
5391  valDK2_13 = 0.0;
5392  valDK2_21 = 0.0;
5393  valDK2_22 = 0.0;
5394  valDK2_23 = 0.0;
5395  valDK2_31 = 0.0;
5396  valDK2_32 = 0.0;
5397  valDK2_33 = 0.0;
5398 
5399  // DN
5400  valDN_11 = 0.0;
5401  valDN_12 = 0.0;
5402  valDN_13 = 0.0;
5403  valDN_21 = 0.0;
5404  valDN_22 = 0.0;
5405  valDN_23 = 0.0;
5406  valDN_31 = 0.0;
5407  valDN_32 = 0.0;
5408  valDN_33 = 0.0;
5409 
5410  // DW
5411  valDW_11 = 0.0;
5412  valDW_12 = 0.0;
5413  valDW_13 = 0.0;
5414  valDW_21 = 0.0;
5415  valDW_22 = 0.0;
5416  valDW_23 = 0.0;
5417  valDW_31 = 0.0;
5418  valDW_32 = 0.0;
5419  valDW_33 = 0.0;
5420 
5421  // DP
5422  valDP_11 = 0.0;
5423  valDP_12 = 0.0;
5424  valDP_13 = 0.0;
5425  valDP_21 = 0.0;
5426  valDP_22 = 0.0;
5427  valDP_23 = 0.0;
5428  valDP_31 = 0.0;
5429  valDP_32 = 0.0;
5430  valDP_33 = 0.0;
5431 
5432  // DM
5433  valDM_11 = 0.0;
5434  valDM_12 = 0.0;
5435  valDM_13 = 0.0;
5436  valDM_21 = 0.0;
5437  valDM_22 = 0.0;
5438  valDM_23 = 0.0;
5439  valDM_31 = 0.0;
5440  valDM_32 = 0.0;
5441  valDM_33 = 0.0;
5442 
5443  for (int k = 0; k < dPhiU->size(); k++)
5444  {
5445  // DK1
5446  valDK1_11 = valDK1_11 + weights->at(k) *
5447  ( 2 * u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5448  ( u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5449  ( u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5450  valDK1_12 = valDK1_12 + weights->at(k) *
5451  ( 2 * u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5452  ( u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5453  ( u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5454  valDK1_13 = valDK1_13 + weights->at(k) *
5455  ( 2 * u13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5456  ( u13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5457  ( u13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5458  valDK1_21 = valDK1_21 + weights->at(k) *
5459  ( ( u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5460  2 * u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5461  ( u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5462  valDK1_22 = valDK1_22 + weights->at(k) *
5463  ( ( u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5464  2 * u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5465  ( u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5466  valDK1_23 = valDK1_23 + weights->at(k) *
5467  ( ( u23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5468  2 * u23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5469  ( u23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + u33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5470  valDK1_31 = valDK1_31 + weights->at(k) *
5471  ( ( u31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5472  ( u31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] ) +
5473  2 * u31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5474  valDK1_32 = valDK1_32 + weights->at(k) *
5475  ( ( u32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5476  ( u32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] ) +
5477  2 * u32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5478  valDK1_33 = valDK1_33 + weights->at(k) *
5479  ( ( u33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] + u13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5480  ( u33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + u23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] ) +
5481  2 * u33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2];
5482 
5483  // DK2
5484  valDK2_11 = valDK2_11 + weights->at(k) *
5485  ( ( -sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - sigma13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5486  sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5487  sigma13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5488  valDK2_12 = valDK2_12 + weights->at(k) *
5489  ( sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5490  ( -sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5491  sigma13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5492  valDK2_13 = valDK2_13 + weights->at(k) *
5493  ( sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5494  sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5495  ( -sigma11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5496  valDK2_21 = valDK2_21 + weights->at(k) *
5497  ( ( -sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - sigma23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5498  sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5499  sigma23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5500  valDK2_22 = valDK2_22 + weights->at(k) *
5501  ( sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5502  ( -sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5503  sigma23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5504  valDK2_23 = valDK2_23 + weights->at(k) *
5505  ( sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5506  sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5507  ( -sigma21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5508  valDK2_31 = valDK2_31 + weights->at(k) *
5509  ( ( -sigma32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - sigma33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5510  sigma32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5511  sigma33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5512  valDK2_32 = valDK2_32 + weights->at(k) *
5513  ( sigma31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5514  ( -sigma31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5515  sigma33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5516  valDK2_33 = valDK2_33 + weights->at(k) *
5517  ( sigma31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][0] +
5518  sigma32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * dPhiTransU[k][i][1] +
5519  ( -sigma31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - sigma32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] ) * dPhiTransU[k][i][2] );
5520 
5521  // DN
5522  double ZN_11; // Die Z_i fuer das DN wie in der Masterarbeit definiert
5523  double ZN_12;
5524  double ZN_13;
5525  double ZN_21;
5526  double ZN_22;
5527  double ZN_23;
5528  double ZN_31;
5529  double ZN_32;
5530  double ZN_33;
5531  ZN_11 = - ( u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - ( u3Loc[0][k] - w3Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][2];
5532  ZN_12 = ( u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0];
5533  ZN_13 = ( u3Loc[0][k] - w3Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0];
5534  ZN_21 = ( u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1];
5535  ZN_22 = - ( u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - ( u3Loc[0][k] - w3Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][2];
5536  ZN_23 = ( u3Loc[0][k] - w3Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1];
5537  ZN_31 = ( u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][2];
5538  ZN_32 = ( u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][2];
5539  ZN_33 = - ( u1Loc[0][k] - w1Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] - ( u2Loc[0][k] - w2Loc[0][k] ) * dPhiTransU[k][j][1];
5540 
5541  valDN_11 = valDN_11 + weights->at(k) *
5542  ( ZN_11 * u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5543  ZN_12 * u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5544  ZN_13 * u13[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5545  valDN_12 = valDN_12 + weights->at(k) *
5546  ( ZN_21 * u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5547  ZN_22 * u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5548  ZN_23 * u13[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5549  valDN_13 = valDN_13 + weights->at(k) *
5550  ( ZN_31 * u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5551  ZN_32 * u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5552  ZN_33 * u13[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5553  valDN_21 = valDN_21 + weights->at(k) *
5554  ( ZN_11 * u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5555  ZN_12 * u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5556  ZN_13 * u23[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5557  valDN_22 = valDN_22 + weights->at(k) *
5558  ( ZN_21 * u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5559  ZN_22 * u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5560  ZN_23 * u23[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5561  valDN_23 = valDN_23 + weights->at(k) *
5562  ( ZN_31 * u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5563  ZN_32 * u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5564  ZN_33 * u23[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5565  valDN_31 = valDN_31 + weights->at(k) *
5566  ( ZN_11 * u31[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5567  ZN_12 * u32[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5568  ZN_13 * u33[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5569  valDN_32 = valDN_32 + weights->at(k) *
5570  ( ZN_21 * u31[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5571  ZN_22 * u32[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5572  ZN_23 * u33[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5573  valDN_33 = valDN_33 + weights->at(k) *
5574  ( ZN_31 * u31[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5575  ZN_32 * u32[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) +
5576  ZN_33 * u33[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5577 
5578  // DW
5579  valDW_11 = valDW_11 + weights->at(k) *
5580  ( u11[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5581  valDW_12 = valDW_12 + weights->at(k) *
5582  ( u12[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5583  valDW_13 = valDW_13 + weights->at(k) *
5584  ( u13[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5585  valDW_21 = valDW_21 + weights->at(k) *
5586  ( u21[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5587  valDW_22 = valDW_22 + weights->at(k) *
5588  ( u22[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5589  valDW_23 = valDW_23 + weights->at(k) *
5590  ( u23[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5591  valDW_31 = valDW_31 + weights->at(k) *
5592  ( u31[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5593  valDW_32 = valDW_32 + weights->at(k) *
5594  ( u32[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5595  valDW_33 = valDW_33 + weights->at(k) *
5596  ( u33[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(j) * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5597 
5598  // DP
5599  double ZP_1; // Die Z_i fuer das DP wie in der Masterarbeit definiert
5600  double ZP_2;
5601  double ZP_3;
5602  ZP_1 = -w21[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] + w22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] -
5603  w31[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + w33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0];
5604  ZP_2 = w11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1] - w12[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] -
5605  w32[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] + w33[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1];
5606  ZP_3 = w11[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] - w13[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][0] +
5607  w22[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][2] - w23[0][k] * dPhiTransU[k][j][1];
5608 
5609  valDP_11 = valDP_11 + weights->at(k) *
5610  ( ZP_1 * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5611  valDP_12 = valDP_12 + weights->at(k) *
5612  ( ZP_2 * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5613  valDP_13 = valDP_13 + weights->at(k) *
5614  ( ZP_3 * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5615  valDP_21 = valDP_21 + weights->at(k) *
5616  ( ZP_1 * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5617  valDP_22 = valDP_22 + weights->at(k) *
5618  ( ZP_2 * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5619  valDP_23 = valDP_23 + weights->at(k) *
5620  ( ZP_3 * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5621  valDP_31 = valDP_31 + weights->at(k) *
5622  ( ZP_1 * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5623  valDP_32 = valDP_32 + weights->at(k) *
5624  ( ZP_2 * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5625  valDP_33 = valDP_33 + weights->at(k) *
5626  ( ZP_3 * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5627 
5628  // DM
5629  valDM_11 = valDM_11 + weights->at(k) *
5630  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5631  valDM_12 = valDM_12 + weights->at(k) *
5632  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5633  valDM_13 = valDM_13 + weights->at(k) *
5634  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * u1Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5635  valDM_21 = valDM_21 + weights->at(k) *
5636  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5637  valDM_22 = valDM_22 + weights->at(k) *
5638  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5639  valDM_23 = valDM_23 + weights->at(k) *
5640  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * u2Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5641  valDM_31 = valDM_31 + weights->at(k) *
5642  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][0] * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5643  valDM_32 = valDM_32 + weights->at(k) *
5644  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][1] * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5645  valDM_33 = valDM_33 + weights->at(k) *
5646  ( dPhiTransU[k][j][2] * u3Loc[0][k] * phiU->at(k).at(i) );
5647  }
5648 
5649  val11 = -rho*nu*valDK1_11 + valDK2_11 + rho*valDN_11 - rho*valDP_11 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_11 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_11;
5650  val12 = -rho*nu*valDK1_12 + valDK2_12 + rho*valDN_12 - rho*valDP_12 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_12 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_12;
5651  val13 = -rho*nu*valDK1_13 + valDK2_13 + rho*valDN_13 - rho*valDP_13 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_13 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_13;
5652  val21 = -rho*nu*valDK1_21 + valDK2_21 + rho*valDN_21 - rho*valDP_21 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_21 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_21;
5653  val22 = -rho*nu*valDK1_22 + valDK2_22 + rho*valDN_22 - rho*valDP_22 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_22 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_22;
5654  val23 = -rho*nu*valDK1_23 + valDK2_23 + rho*valDN_23 - rho*valDP_23 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_23 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_23;
5655  val31 = -rho*nu*valDK1_31 + valDK2_31 + rho*valDN_31 - rho*valDP_31 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_31 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_31;
5656  val32 = -rho*nu*valDK1_32 + valDK2_32 + rho*valDN_32 - rho*valDP_32 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_32 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_32;
5657  val33 = -rho*nu*valDK1_33 + valDK2_33 + rho*valDN_33 - rho*valDP_33 - (1.0/dt)*rho*valDW_33 + (0.5/dt)*rho*valDM_33;
5658 
5659  val11 = absDetB * val11;
5660  val12 = absDetB * val12;
5661  val13 = absDetB * val13;
5662  val21 = absDetB * val21;
5663  val22 = absDetB * val22;
5664  val23 = absDetB * val23;
5665  val31 = absDetB * val31;
5666  val32 = absDetB * val32;
5667  val33 = absDetB * val33;
5668 
5669  value11[0] = val11; // x-x
5670  value12[0] = val12; // x-y
5671  value13[0] = val13; // x-z
5672  value21[0] = val21; // y-x
5673  value22[0] = val22; // y-y
5674  value23[0] = val23; // y-z
5675  value31[0] = val31; // z-x
5676  value32[0] = val32; // z-y
5677  value33[0] = val33; // z-z
5678 
5679 
5680  glob_j = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(j));
5681  glob_i = dim * map->getGlobalElement(elements->getElement(T).getNode(i));
5682  indices[0] = glob_j;
5683 
5684  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value11()); // x-x
5685  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value21()); // y-x
5686  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value31()); // z-x
5687  glob_j++;
5688  indices[0] = glob_j;
5689  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value12()); // x-y
5690  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value22()); // y-y
5691  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value32()); // z-y
5692  glob_j++;
5693  indices[0] = glob_j;
5694  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i, indices(), value13()); // x-z
5695  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+1, indices(), value23()); // y-z
5696  D->insertGlobalValues(glob_i+2, indices(), value33()); // z-z
5697  }
5698  }
5699  }
5700  if (callFillComplete)
5701  {
5702  D->fillComplete();
5703  }
5704  }
5705 
5706 }
